{"_id":"AwaSwcf1rfnJT3QY","name":"James the Swordsman","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/james-el-espadachin.webp","items":[{"_id":"oBnRzBLlOBjOWFzk","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>H e sido muchas cosas en mi vida: capitán de barco, duelista de gran <br>renombre y amante de las nobles más bellas. Tras años de éxitos y victorias, un misterioso niño me derrotó con engaños. Este despreciable <br>muchacho me condujo a la guarida de una peligrosa bestia y, tras apre<br>-sarme, me dejó para que me devorara el monstruo. Sobreviví, aunque <br>perdí una mano... Tengo la certeza de que aquel a quien busco no es hu<br>-mano, y me uní a la Orden para dar caza al niño que odio por encima de <br>todo y así vengarme.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FbRoxNfHphsyNXQd","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy un hábil espadachín y tengo buenos modales, por lo que la <br>Orden me considera un excelente candidato para moverme entre <br>la alta sociedad. Me encanta deleitarme con la buena comida y la <br>compañía alegre.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"voh4Dv5hlkyFqea1","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>He aprendido a enfrentarme a monstruos y aberraciones sin dejarme intimidar. La Bestia me sigue el rastro porque, habiendo <br>probado mi carne, ya no puede prescindir de ella...</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"w3wtU6GHaC3Am1te","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Jaime<br>el Espadachín<br>Soy un hombre de mundo y ya nada puede sorprenderme. Nunca me <br>cuestiono a mí mismo. Al fin y al cabo, soy el mejor en lo que <br>hago.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MYixdaMasYytbl8M","name":"With a Sword or a Smile","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Con una espada o una sonrisa","description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes realizar un movimiento de extrema precisión con tu arma, como <br>quitarle un objeto a alguien o escribir algo en una superficie. La per -<br>sona que observe tu habilidad quedará impresionada o intimidada, <br>según decida el Narrador. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilizas <br>en tu beneficio la emoción que has despertado.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you may perform a gesture of extreme precision with your weapon, such as slipping an object off someone or writing something on a surface. The person observing your skill will either be impressed or intimidated, depending on the Storyteller’s decision. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the emotion you have aroused to your advantage.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"n3OPAa2woT0r4kmA","name":"Tick-Tock, Here Comes The Beast","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Tic-tac, ya viene la bestia","description":"<p>mientras estás al aire libre, <br>puedes pedirle al Narrador que la Bestia venga en busca de tu carne.<br>La Bestia es un PNJ monstruoso con las siguientes características:<br>NO Difícil 7 – (4 Heridas) <br>Descriptor: soy una bestia grande y poderosa. Arrollo todo lo que encuentro en mi camino para poder atrapar a mi presa.<br>Don – Locura voraz: la Bestia tiene un ansia enfermiza por tu carne, <br>y desatará su furia sobre cualquiera que se interponga en su camino. <br>Con su titánica fuerza, puede derribar árboles y muros, y lanzar a un <br>hombre por los aires con un solo golpe de sus enormes patas. También <br>es un poco boba y abandonará la escena en cuanto te pierda de vista. <br>Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales en cualquier prueba de Defensa contra <br>ella. Si la Bestia sufre la cuarta Herida, se disolverá. No obstante, se <br>regenerará y podrá utilizarse en la siguiente escena.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"While outdoors, you may ask the Storyteller for the Beast to come in search of your flesh. The Beast is a monstrous NPC with the following characteristics: OL Hard 7 – (4 Wounds).\n\nDescriptor (the Beast): I am a great and mighty beast. I overwhelm everything I come across on my way to snatch my prey.\n\nGift – Ravenous Madness: The Beast has an insane craving for your flesh, and will unleash its rage on anyone standing in its way. With its titanic strength, it can tear down trees and walls, and hurl a man away with a single swipe of its huge paws. The Beast is also quite stupid and will leave the Scene as soon as you are out of sight. You receive 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check against it. If the Beast suffers the fourth Wound, it will dissolve. However, it will regenerate and can be used in the next Scene.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jQ8Bs3Pn0a1yJY64","name":"Dark Ego - I Will Have My Satisfaction","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – Tendré mi recompensa","description":"<p>cuando <br>eliges a un oponente, ya no tiene escapatoria. Una vez por escena, puedes <br>realizar una acción adicional contra el objetivo de tu desafío (incluso si <br>ya habías actuado durante este intercambio) para anticiparte a su movimiento y detener su acción con la tuya. Si un oponente te inflige una <br>Herida, disfrutas del sabor del desafío y obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en las <br>pruebas que realices contra ese oponente durante el resto de la escena.</p>","trigger":"desafías a un enemigo o dejas claro de algún otro modo \nquién eres y el nivel de tus habilidades."}}}},"system":{"description":"When you choose an opponent, there is no escape for them. Once per Scene, you can take an additional action against the target of your challenge (even if you had already acted during this Exchange) to anticipate their move and stop their action with yours. If an opponent inflicts a Wound on you, you savor the taste of the challenge and receive 1 Additional Success at each Check against them for the rest of the Scenario.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You challenge an enemy or otherwise make clear who and how skilled you are.","owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7b5zj6diCyIqRCxz","name":"A fine dueling blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una excelente espada de duelo","description":"<p>Una excelente espada de duelo</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A fine dueling blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jRoEKUjsTbXHVqDe","name":"a black powder gun","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una pistola de pólvora negra","description":"<p>Una pistola de pólvora negra</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a black powder gun","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9btiuzzEaOQFQfRC","name":"a finely crafted hook","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un garfio finamente elaborado","description":"<p>Un garfio finamente elaborado</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a finely crafted hook","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"uOg5YKmgcQ2H5pA7","name":"a purple-red cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una capa de color rojo púrpura","description":"<p>Una capa de color rojo púrpura</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a purple-red cloak","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zTLzCH8dRlSjfAdg","name":"traveling boots","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Botas de viaje","description":"<p>Botas de viaje</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"traveling boots","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7qVpBt9511Yf2kTr","name":"a precious pair of binoculars","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Unos preciosos prismáticos","description":"<p>Unos preciosos prismáticos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a precious pair of binoculars","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rsnVlbomcSuf5IEn","name":"several valuable rings","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"equipment","sequence":7,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Anillos valiosos.","description":"<p>Anillos valiosos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"several valuable rings","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1iA7CrDYeOQBfIUT","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4","owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-james-the-swordsman","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"4","contentKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Jaime el Espadachín","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Jaime el Espadachín","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>H e sido muchas cosas en mi vida: capitán de barco, duelista de gran <br>renombre y amante de las nobles más bellas. Tras años de éxitos y victorias, un misterioso niño me derrotó con engaños. Este despreciable <br>muchacho me condujo a la guarida de una peligrosa bestia y, tras apre<br>-sarme, me dejó para que me devorara el monstruo. Sobreviví, aunque <br>perdí una mano... Tengo la certeza de que aquel a quien busco no es hu<br>-mano, y me uní a la Orden para dar caza al niño que odio por encima de <br>todo y así vengarme.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"James the Swordsman","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PbUHEd7k5B71k7TB","name":"Garou the Old Wolf","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/garou-el-viejo-lobo.webp","items":[{"_id":"swezn8BMBBnIZThV","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Pero no soy tan viejo como para no poder enfrentarme a los que más me odian, <br>aunque me den caza y me vilipendien. Ahora que formo parte de la Orden, uso mi <br>fuerza para defender a los débiles cazadores que son mis compañeros, sabiendo <br>que con un solo mordisco podría acabar con sus insignificantes vidas.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Soy un lobo de montaña, mucho más astuto que los estúpidos aldeanos que tiemblan solo con verme. He vivido orgulloso a la cabeza de mi manada, liderando mil incursiones y comiendo suculentos y tiernos bocados de carne humana. Pero no soy tan viejo como para no poder enfrentarme a los que más me odian, aunque me den caza y me vilipendien. Ahora que formo parte de la Orden, uso mi fuerza para defender a los débiles cazadores que son mis compañeros, sabiendo que con un solo mordisco podría acabar con sus insignificantes vidas.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pfHYMfOaq00NjZ8J","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Mis sentidos son infalibles. Nada puede escapar a mi olfato y <br>por eso la Orden me utiliza como guardián. Odio los olores <br>y los ruidos fuertes porque son como hierros candentes para <br>mis agudos sentidos.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Mis sentidos son infalibles. Nada puede escapar a mi olfato y por eso la Orden me utiliza como guardián. Odio los olores y los ruidos fuertes porque son como hierros candentes para mis agudos sentidos.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UtFN1p2V3bBjvLMe","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Un verdadero depredador sabe mostrarse como el más indefenso de los corderos. Yo sé cómo disfrazarme. Mi confianza <br>es ilimitada y a menudo tiendo a subestimar el peligro, dispuesto a arriesgarme a todo por un sabroso bocado.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Un verdadero depredador sabe mostrarse como el más indefenso de los corderos. Yo sé cómo disfrazarme. Mi confianza es ilimitada y a menudo tiendo a subestimar el peligro, dispuesto a arriesgarme a todo por un sabroso bocado.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"khTJtje3L5vNVALW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Soy más feroz y poderoso que cualquier humano y mis colmillos <br>pueden atravesar incluso el metal. Mi orgulloso espíritu de lobo <br>lo es todo para mí.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Soy más feroz y poderoso que cualquier humano y mis colmillos pueden atravesar incluso el metal. Mi orgulloso espíritu de lobo lo es todo para mí.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JB6guX7xUoG9SIQT","name":"Find Them Forever After","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Encontrarlos para siempre","description":"<p>cuando percibes el olor de <br>alguien, nunca lo olvidas. Durante una escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma <br>para memorizar el olor de una persona con la que estés interactuando. <br>La reconocerás siempre y te será fácil seguir su rastro incluso después <br>de algún tiempo. Si te concentras, puedes oír un ruido incluso a grandes distancias. Cuando alguien se te acerque, el Narrador te avisará <br>mucho antes de que cualquiera en la escena se dé cuenta.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Cuando percibes el olor de alguien, nunca lo olvidas. Durante una escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma para memorizar el olor de una persona con la que estás interactuando. La reconocerás siempre y te será fácil seguir su rastro incluso después de algún tiempo. Si te concentras, puedes oír un ruido incluso a grandes distancias. Cuando alguien se te acerque, el Narrador te avisará mucho antes de que cualquiera en la escena se dé cuenta.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"Once you catch someone’s scent, you never forget it. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to memorize the scent of a person you are interacting with. You will always recognize it and it will be easy for you to follow its traces even after some time. If you concentrate, you can hear a noise even at great distances. When someone approaches you, the Storyteller will warn you long before anyone else in the Scene would notice.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HG71as6x89jNnY8v","name":"Wolf Among the Lambs","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Lobo entre los corderos","description":"<p>puedes gastar 1 Soma para <br>adoptar la forma de un humano común. Crea un descriptor que <br>te represente y que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Viejo, <br>Indefenso, Débil. En tu forma humana puedes hablar y actuar <br>sin problemas, pero, en cuanto utilices tu ego Oscuro, perderás <br>inmediatamente el efecto de Lobo entre los corderos. Obtienes 1 <br>Éxito adicional cuando utilizas el descriptor que has creado para <br>engañar a alguien y pillarle desprevenido.<br>S oy un lobo de montaña, mucho más astuto que los estúpidos aldeanos que <br>tiemblan solo con verme. He vivido orgulloso a la cabeza de mi manada, liderando mil incursiones y comiendo suculentos y tiernos bocados de carne humana.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Puedes gastar 1 Soma para adoptar la forma de un humano común. Crea un descriptor que te represente y que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Viejo, Indefenso, Débil. En tu forma humana puedes hablar y actuar sin problemas, pero, en cuanto utilices tu ego Oscuro, perderás inmediatamente el efecto de Lobo entre los corderos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilizas el descriptor que has creado para engañar a alguien y pillarle desprevenido.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"You may spend 1 Soma to assume the shape of a common human. Create a Descriptor that represents you and includes at least one of these words: Old, Helpless, Weak. In your human form you can speak and act without problems, but, as soon as you use your Dark Ego, you will immediately lose the effect of Wolf Among the Lambs. You receive 1 Additional Success when you use the Descriptor you created to deceive someone and catch them off guard.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yzG7ReEiGvukOZac","name":"Dark Ego - The Big Bad Wolf","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - El gran lobo feroz","description":"<p>llevas toda una vida en las <br>grandes montañas y tu destreza solo es comparable a tu valentía. Cuando <br>desates tu furia, crea un descriptor para ella que incluya al menos una <br>de estas palabras: Fuerte, Feroz, Imparable. Puedes emplear la fuerza <br>de tres hombres, roer la piedra con la misma facilidad que la carne o derribar cualquier barrera. Cuando actúas usando este descriptor especial <br>para pruebas de posición, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional. Una vez por escena, <br>puedes desatar tu furia y obtener 3 Éxitos adicionales en lugar de 1.</p>","trigger":"adoptas la forma de un lobo o te revelas como lo que realmente eres, asustando a los humanos débiles.","system":{"description":"<p>Llevas toda una vida en las grandes montañas y tu destreza solo es comparable a tu valentía. Cuando desates tu furia, crea un descriptor para ella que incluya al menos una de estas palabras: Fuerte, Feroz, Imparable. Puedes emplear la fuerza de tres hombres, roer la piedra con la misma facilidad que la carne o derribar cualquier barrera. Cuando actúas usando este descriptor especial para pruebas de posición, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional. Una vez por escena, puedes desatar tu furia y obtener 3 Éxitos adicionales en lugar de 1.</p>","trigger":"adoptas la forma de un lobo o te revelas como lo que realmente eres, asustando a los humanos débiles."}}}}},"system":{"description":"You are hardened by a lifetime in the great mountains and your skill is matched only by your courage. When you unleash your rage, create a Descriptor for it that includes at least one of these words: Strong, Fierce, Unstoppable. You can employ the strength of three men, gnaw through stone as easily as flesh, or break down any barrier. When you act using this special Descriptor for Position Checks, you get 1 Additional Success. Once per Scene, you can unleash your rage and receive 3 Additional Successes instead of 1.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You assume the form of a Wolf or reveal yourself for what you really are, scaring off weak humans.","owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S7QdHzjDvLSdrUxK","name":"Fangs and claws (natural weapons)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Colmillos y garras","description":"<p>Un collar de piedras y madera que llevo en una pata, recuerdo del único humano al que no considero comida</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Colmillos y garras.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"Fangs and claws (natural weapons)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OZ2YJLQLRIGHMzUZ","name":"a necklace of stones and wood that I carry in a paw—token of the only human I do not consider food","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un collar de piedras y madera","description":"<p>Baratijas, llaves y otros desperdicios que a veces vomito de mi gran estómago.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Un collar de piedras y madera que llevo en una pata, recuerdo del único humano al que no considero comida.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"a necklace of stones and wood that I carry in a paw—token of the only human I do not consider food","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NoQ4edZFAfc3MrkF","name":"knick-knacks, keys, and other junk that I sometimes vomit up from my large stomach","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Baratijas, llaves y otros desperdicios","system":{"description":"<p>Baratijas, llaves y otros desperdicios que a veces vomito de mi gran estómago.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"knick-knacks, keys, and other junk that I sometimes vomit up from my large stomach","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Oji0UJEJxlSLwzIt","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6","owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-garou-the-old-wolf","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"6","contentKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Garou el Viejo Lobo","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Soy un lobo de montaña, mucho más astuto que los estúpidos aldeanos que tiemblan solo con verme. He vivido orgulloso a la cabeza de mi manada, liderando mil incursiones y comiendo suculentos y tiernos bocados de carne humana. Pero no soy tan viejo como para no poder enfrentarme a los que más me odian, aunque me den caza y me vilipendien. Ahora que formo parte de la Orden, uso mi fuerza para defender a los débiles cazadores que son mis compañeros, sabiendo que con un solo mordisco podría acabar con sus insignificantes vidas.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Garou the Old Wolf","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"81ZD8w9cdOxjx8yE","name":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/el-asombroso-flautista-sin-nombre.webp","items":[{"_id":"YOrMShr5kOrjAmNq","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Siempre he hecho de mi arte mi razón de vivir. Puedo tocar con tanta destreza que es como si fuera magia. He aprendido a utilizar el poder de la música para llegar al alma de los seres humanos y de los animales. Por desgracia, he perdido la cuenta de las veces que he realizado actos deshonrosos mientras perseguía la melodía perfecta. Tras haber sido culpable de varios crímenes y haberme vengado de quienes se burlaban de mi sincero amor por la música, esperé serenamente mi ejecución. La Orden me liberó a cambio de la promesa de servirles y poner mis habilidades al servicio de la lucha contra la Oscuridad. Fue en los momentos más oscuros cuando vislumbré la melodía perfecta, así que quizá, como Cazador, pueda encontrarla y hacerla mía.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CD4xvppWZDR7UOmP","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Música del alma","description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Con mi flauta puedo tocar cualquier melodía y llegar al corazón de los seres vivos. El arte necesita tiempo para expresarse.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vNRlSVZvG5vwJ74V","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Acróbata experto","description":"<p>Soy acróbata y músico. Mi talento es incomparable y la Orden <br>me ha elegido por mi capacidad para captar la atención de la <br>gente y estimular sus emociones. Cuando me invade la inspiración artística, me alejo totalmente de la realidad.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Soy acróbata y músico. Mi talento es incomparable y la Orden me ha elegido por mi capacidad para captar la atención de la gente y estimular sus emociones. Cuando me invade la inspiración artística, me alejo totalmente de la realidad.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xfJfFQfgk4rqz3Nn","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Como artista he viajado a muchos lugares y conozco infinidad <br>de mitos y leyendas. Tengo hambre de conocimiento y me fascina <br>todo lo que ignoro.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Como artista he viajado a muchos lugares y conozco infinidad de mitos y leyendas. Tengo hambre de conocimiento y me fascina todo lo que ignoro.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XOlzRBIW7s5J7296","name":"Soul Music","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Música del alma","description":"<p>cuando tocas la flauta, puedes gastar 1 <br>Soma para interpretar una melodía especial. Elige entre:<br>1. Transmitir una emoción: crea un descriptor que represente el <br>estado emocional que quieres transmitir. Todos los presentes recibirán ese descriptor para la escena actual. Puede que tengas que <br>hacer una prueba de Posición para afectar a los oponentes.<br>2. Encantar animales: puedes dar órdenes sencillas a los animales <br>que escuchen tu melodía. Si muestran una actitud agresiva, tienes <br>que superar una prueba de posición para que tu melodía surta efecto. Mientras estés tocando, puedes pedir a los animales que realicen <br>acciones sencillas como moverse o seguir una orden básica.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Cuando tocas la flauta, puedes gastar 1 Soma para interpretar una melodía especial. Elige entre:</p><p>Transmitir una emoción: crea un descriptor que represente lo que quieres transmitir. Todos los presentes recibirán ese descriptor para la escena actual. Puede que tengas que hacer una prueba de Posición para afectar a los oponentes.</p><p>Encantar animales: puedes dar órdenes sencillas a los animales que escuchen tu melodía. Si muestran una actitud agresiva, tienes que superar una prueba de Posición para que tu melodía surta efecto. Mientras estás tocando, puedes pedir a los animales que realicen acciones sencillas como moverse o seguir una orden básica.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"When you play your pipes you can spend 1 Soma to sing a special melody. Choose from:\n1. Imparting an emotion: Create a Descriptor that represents the emotional state you wish to convey. Everybody present will receive that Descriptor for the current Scene. You may have to make a Position Check to affect opponents.\n2. Bewitching animals: You may give simple commands to animals that hear your melody. If they show an aggressive attitude, you have to make a successful Position Check for your melody to take effect. As long as you are playing, you may ask the animals to do simple actions such as moving or following a simple command.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dVrNSOWqzTn3oRT8","name":"Skilled Acrobat","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Acróbata experto","description":"<p>cuando cantas, bailas o te mueves con <br>gracia, siempre das un gran espectáculo. Como acción adicional, <br>puedes gastar 1 Soma y decidir uno de los siguientes efectos:<br>1. Puedes dar un salto increíble, de varios metros de altura, sin que <br>nadie pueda detenerte.<br>2. Puedes apoderarte de un objeto, aunque lo lleve un enemigo.<br>3. Puedes realizar una acción menor con una acrobacia, como <br>abrir una puerta o accionar una palanca, y luego volver exactamente al punto de partida.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Cuando cantas, bailas o te mueves con gracia, siempre das un gran espectáculo. Como acción adicional, puedes gastar 1 Soma y decidir uno de los siguientes efectos:</p><p>Puedes dar un salto increíble, de varios metros de altura, sin que nadie pueda detenerte.</p><p>Puedes apoderarte de un objeto, aunque lo lleve un enemigo.</p><p>Puedes realizar una acción menor con una acrobacia, como abrir una puerta o accionar una palanca, y luego volver exactamente al punto de partida.</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"When you sing, dance, or move with grace, you always put on a great show. As an additional action, you can spend 1 Soma and decide on one of the following effects:\n1. You can make an incredible leap, many feet high, without anyone being able to stop you.\n2. You may take an object, even if it is worn by an enemy.\n3. You can perform a minor action with a stunt, such as opening a door or flipping a switch, and then return exactly to where you started.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KRxcTnlxBVDV6D3f","name":"Dark Ego - The Power of Music","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – El poder de la música","description":"<p>una vez por escena, <br>puedes emitir un sonido que puede percibe quien tú quieras, incluso <br>a gran distancia. Todo el que lo oye sufre 1 Herida, los objetos frágiles <br>se rompen y los animales asustados huyen. Alternativamente, puedes <br>tocar una suave melodía y el propio viento te obedecerá, llevando tu <br>mensaje a quien tú quieras, esté donde esté. Al usar El poder de la <br>música, también puedes activar un efecto de Música del alma en uno <br>o más objetivos de tu elección.</p>","trigger":"demostrar tu arte en toda su extensión, con un espectáculo \nque no se puede pasar por alto.","system":{"description":"<p>Una vez por escena, puedes emitir un sonido que percibe quien tú quieras, incluso a gran distancia. Todo el que lo oye sufre 1 Herida, los objetos frágiles se rompen y los animales asustados huyen. Alternativamente, puedes tocar una suave melodía y el propio viento te obedecerá, llevando tu mensaje a quien tú quieras, esté donde esté. Al usar El poder de la música, también puedes activar un efecto de Música del alma en uno o más objetivos de tu elección.</p>","trigger":"Demostrar tu arte en toda su extensión, con un espectáculo que no se puede pasar por alto."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can make a sound that can be heard by whomever you wish, even from a great distance. Everyone who hears it suffers 1 Wound, fragile objects break, and frightened animals flee. Alternatively, you can play a gentle melody and the wind itself will obey you, carrying your message to whomever you wish, wherever they are. When using The Power of Music, you can also activate a Soul Music effect on one or more targets of your choice.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Demonstrate your art to its fullest extent, with a show that cannot be ignored.","owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Irhx6r5cbTOakDwx","name":"A precious pipe of the finest workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una preciosa flauta de la mejor factura","description":"<p>Una preciosa flauta de la mejor factura</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Una preciosa flauta de la mejor factura</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"A precious pipe of the finest workmanship","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HM6wxp4dNq9cBVvC","name":"a theater mask","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una máscara de teatro","description":"<p>Una máscara de teatro</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Una máscara de teatro</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"a theater mask","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gAlfINBNTIWK7HUb","name":"a cloak of many colors","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una capa de muchos colores","description":"<p>Una capa de muchos colores</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Una capa de muchos colores</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"a cloak of many colors","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"dmhV0hInzrQMRt47","name":"multicolored chalks and powders","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Tizas y polvos multicolores","description":"<p>Tizas y polvos multicolores</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Tizas y polvos multicolores</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"multicolored chalks and powders","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ctc9uoGaCdXqHyxD","name":"an old ocarina (the first instrument I ever played), and Hamelin","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una vieja ocarina, el primer instrumento que toqué","description":"<p>Una vieja ocarina, el primer instrumento que toqué</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Una vieja ocarina, el primer instrumento que toqué</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"an old ocarina (the first instrument I ever played), and Hamelin","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"RzBFK54xqCloBKIn","name":"my faithful trained mouse","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Hamelín, mi fiel ratón amaestrado.","description":"<p>Hamelín, mi fiel ratón amaestrado.</p>","system":{"description":"<p>Hamelín, mi fiel ratón amaestrado</p>"}}}}},"system":{"description":"my faithful trained mouse","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CvaK8tuXmB3On7Xo","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8","owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"8","contentKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"El Asombroso Flautista sin Nombre","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Siempre he hecho de mi arte mi razón de vivir. Puedo tocar con tanta destreza que es como si fuera magia. He aprendido a utilizar el poder de la música para llegar al alma de los seres humanos y de los animales. Por desgracia, he perdido la cuenta de las veces que he realizado actos deshonrosos mientras perseguía la melodía perfecta. Tras haber sido culpable de varios crímenes y haberme vengado de quienes se burlaban de mi sincero amor por la música, esperé serenamente mi ejecución. La Orden me liberó a cambio de la promesa de servirles y poner mis habilidades al servicio de la lucha contra la Oscuridad. Fue en los momentos más oscuros cuando vislumbré la melodía perfecta, así que quizá, como Cazador, pueda encontrarla y hacerla mía.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"GvHlehXezileafN9","name":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/baba-yaga-la-nina-bruja.webp","items":[{"_id":"QpTgAgFaNGEu82d0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Soy una niña bruja, y mi poder solo es equiparable a mi ambición. No tuve infancia, pues nací ya consciente de mis capacidades. A la mayoría les parezco cínica y cruel. Eso es porque no comprenden que <br>son peones, piezas insignificantes en los sangrientos juegos que juegan brujas y brujos. La Orden no me <br>desprecia por mi edad, por eso me ha dado el liderazgo que merezco.<br>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil <br>suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jO3YDCjtoFzjk3Y0","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy una hechicera y mis poderes mágicos me permiten hacer <br>lo que quiera. Necesito el tiempo adecuado para lanzar mis <br>hechizos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9mSUrCOOFkerpgAQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Soy muy hábil analizando a la gente, por eso la Orden me ha <br>elegido como líder de los Cazadores. Me encanta manipular a <br>la gente y a menudo lo hago solo para divertirme.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4gjBRl2T22GV3iMC","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil <br>suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"59GJpsdUTP17NYKJ","name":"Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Magia","description":"<p>cuando quieras conseguir algo, puedes utilizar la <br>brujería. Elige lo que quieres con una frase como: quiero volar <br>con esa vieja escoba, o quiero parecer un demonio ante esos necios. Tu hechizo debe centrarse en un objeto que tengas, como <br>una escoba para volar o una máscara que puedas usar para parecer un demonio. Paga un coste de 0 a 2 de Soma, decidido por <br>el Narrador, para activar el hechizo durante una escena. Recuerda <br>que no puedes pedir la muerte fulminante de alguien, pero sí infligir Heridas con tus acciones a través de la magia.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"When you want to achieve something, you may use witchcraft. Choose what you want with a sentence like: I want to fly on that old broom, or I want to look like a demon in the eyes of those fools. Your spell must be focused on an object in your possession, such as a broom to fly or a mask you can wear to look like a demon. Pay a cost from 0 to 2 Soma, decided by the Storyteller, to activate your spell for the duration of a Scene. Remember that you can’t ask for someone’s sudden death, but you can inflict Wounds with your actions through magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"27yYZcpuEIgUvZiZ","name":"Listen to my Words","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Escucha mis palabras","description":"<p>una vez por escena, cuando hables con alguien, puedes hacer una pregunta al Narrador sobre esa <br>persona. La pregunta debe referirse a su comportamiento, como <br>sus vicios o sus deseos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier <br>acción en la que explotes lo que has descubierto.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you talk to someone, you can ask the Storyteller a question about them. The question must be regarding their behaviour, such as any vices or their desires they might have. You gain 1 Additional Success in any action where you exploit what you’ve discovered.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sOM18jLiBg4qlrD5","name":"Dark Ego - The Evil Witch","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - La bruja malvada","description":"<p>obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba cuando utilices uno de tus hechizos, ya sea a través del don Magia <br>o introduciéndolo en tu narración a través de los descriptores. Además, puedes <br>desatar tu aura maligna para obtener uno o más de los siguientes efectos:<br>1. Los animales y la gente corriente se sienten atormentados por tu presencia y huirán despavoridos.<br>2. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional si utilizas tu magia para castigar a alguien <br>por romper una promesa o un acuerdo alcanzado anteriormente.<br>3. En el área que te rodea, puedes convocar la luz del día o la oscuridad.</p>","trigger":"Asustar a la gente corriente o imponer castigos a través de tu \nmagia."}}}},"system":{"description":"Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check when you use one of your spells, either through the Magic Gift or by inserting it into your narrative through the Descriptors. Moreover, you can unleash your evil aura to gain one or more of the following effects:\n1. Animals and ordinary people are tormented by your presence and will flee in terror.\n2. You gain 1 Additional Success if you use your magic to punish someone for breaking a promise or agreement you made earlier.\n3. In the area around you, you can summon daylight or darkness.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Scare ordinary people or dispense punishment through your magic.","owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NjAGtq8vlONgvPHA","name":"An old and worn-out black cloak","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una vieja y gastada capa negra","description":"<p>Una vieja y gastada capa negra</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"An old and worn-out black cloak","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YwZrsYB67QscAl3u","name":"a bag of magical ingredients","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una bolsa de ingredientes mágicos","description":"<p>Una bolsa de ingredientes mágicos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a bag of magical ingredients","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OVEvcHvIngQVeSAj","name":"a small curved dagger","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una pequeña daga curva","description":"<p>Una pequeña daga curva</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a small curved dagger","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hoYEyIrpu2kEbpt9","name":"a rag doll","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una muñeca de trapo","description":"<p>Una muñeca de trapo</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a rag doll","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"O40QDjrmaPL4j2B2","name":"the Ring of the Order","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El anillo de la Orden","description":"<p>El anillo de la Orden</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"the Ring of the Order","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"R7Bnu9rWcJCZZfRJ","name":"a lucky elderberry branch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una rama de saúco de la suerte","description":"<p>Una rama de saúco de la suerte</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a lucky elderberry branch","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QnYK8fSToDMGjWvc","name":"the keys of a strange hut in a tree which is always in my vicinity","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"equipment","sequence":7,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Las llaves de una extraña cabaña en un árbol, que siempre está en mis cercanías.","description":"<p>Las llaves de una extraña cabaña en un árbol, que siempre está en mis cercanías.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"the keys of a strange hut in a tree which is always in my vicinity","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Qt7vYBSEbQf8Aso5","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10","owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-baba-yaga-the-child-witch","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"10","contentKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Baba Yaga la Niña Bruja","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Soy una niña bruja, y mi poder solo es equiparable a mi ambición. No tuve infancia, pues nací ya consciente de mis capacidades. A la mayoría les parezco cínica y cruel. Eso es porque no comprenden que <br>son peones, piezas insignificantes en los sangrientos juegos que juegan brujas y brujos. La Orden no me <br>desprecia por mi edad, por eso me ha dado el liderazgo que merezco.<br>Como cualquier hechicera respetable, llevo mi fiel bolsa llena de hierbas, venenos y todo tipo de herramientas mágicas. Mi aspecto infantil <br>suele ser útil, pero a veces hace que los demás me subestimen. Odio eso.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3k5iyzmyl7bCNYjJ","name":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/regina-la-ladrona-de-corazones.webp","items":[{"_id":"Q7ODOGHT5IRSzWeQ","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Nací para ser líder y siempre me he rodeado de fieles seguidores dispuestos a satisfacer todos mis <br>caprichos. Al carecer del beneficio de la nobleza de nacimiento, el poder que ostentaba lo arreba -<br>taba de las manos de quienes menos merecían ejercerlo, sin importar el coste. Goberné ejércitos <br>de matones y rompí los corazones de hombres y mujeres. Tras cada conquista, partía en busca de <br>un desafío mayor. Como todavía hay mucho ahí fuera que debería ser mío por derecho, siempre <br>quiero más. La Orden me ha dado un nuevo propósito, una nueva perspectiva y nuevas criaturas <br>a las que esclavizar.<br>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar <br>en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca <br>paso desapercibida.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7T6bK3BsEyh5DGbT","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Estoy decidida a conseguir lo que quiero, y nada se interpondrá <br>en mi camino. Mataré, humillaré o conquistaré a cualquiera o <br>cualquier cosa que se interponga entre mi objetivo y yo. Como <br>puedes imaginar, ¡odio sinceramente que me digan que no!</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MHmRt7uCCq7HGsC8","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Gracias a mis contactos y a mi carisma, siempre tengo un as <br>en la manga: seguidores dispuestos a ayudarme y aliados que <br>me deben favores. Mantener un imperio de conexiones beneficiosas requiere compromiso y recursos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4Sl56nxGWNNjFFAP","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar <br>en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca <br>paso desapercibida.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KddcDJJ0yAaururL","name":"I Want It!","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"¡Lo quiero!","description":"<p>cuando actúas con una intención clara y directa para lograr un objetivo, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas <br>las pruebas de posición. Una vez por sesión, puedes convertir un <br>fracaso en un triunfo con un incremento. Describe cómo haces <br>rechinar los dientes y luchas para conseguir lo que quieres.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"When you act with clear and direct intention to achieve an objective, you get 1 Additional Success on each Position Check. Once per Session, you can turn a Failure into an Outcome with Increment. Describe how you grit your teeth and fight to get what you want.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MHJv5ETZx5P4d9h3","name":"The Queen","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Reina","description":"<p>durante una escena siempre tienes un par de <br>sirvientes de confianza contigo, listos para ejecutar tus órdenes. <br>Crea un descriptor para cada uno, representando la habilidad por <br>la que los tienes a tu servicio. Harán todo lo posible para satisfacer <br>tus deseos. Decide cómo pagarles. El Narrador, cuando y si lo considera necesario, te pedirá que honres sus servicios para no perder <br>el uso de este don durante el resto de la escena. Puedes realizar <br>varias pruebas con este descriptor para obtener PX.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"During a Scene you always have a couple of trusted servants with you, ready to execute your every order. Create a Descriptor for each, which represents the skill for which you hold them in your service. Your servants will do their best to satisfy your every wish. Decide how you pay them. The Storyteller, when and if they deem it necessary, will ask you to honor their services so as not to lose the use of this Gift for the rest of the Scene. You can check this Descriptor multiple times to get XP.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yj3qklCqD7TTrdF2","name":"Dark Ego - As I Want!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - ¡Como yo lo mando!","description":"<p>sabes que tu camino es <br>el único correcto para hacer las cosas. Durante la escena, como acción <br>adicional, puedes elegir a otro personaje al que le darás una <br>orden. En el <br>caso de un aliado, si hace exactamente lo que le dices, recibirá 1 Éxito adicional para su acción o aumentará su Nivel de Oposición en 1. Si das una <br>orden imperativa para atrapar a un enemigo, bajará su Nivel de Oposición <br>en 1 o, si ya lo has visto en acción, puedes impedir que use uno de sus <br>dones. Una vez por escena, puedes gritar, atrayendo la atención de todos <br>hacia ti. Durante unos instantes, harán una pausa para escuchar lo que <br>tienes que decir.</p>","trigger":"tomar el control de una situación e imponer tus decisiones llamando la atención de forma espectacular."}}}},"system":{"description":"You know that your way is the only right way to do things. During the Scene, as an additional action, you can choose another character who will be issued a command. In the case of an ally, if they do exactly what you tell them, they will receive 1 Additional Success to their action or increase their Opposition Level by 1. If you give a peremptory order to ensnare an enemy, they will lower their Opposition Level by 1 or, if you’ve already seen it in action, you can prevent them from using one of their Gifts. Once per Scene, you can shout, drawing everyone’s attention to you. For a few moments, they will pause to listen to what you have to say.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take control of a situation and impose your decisions by dramatically drawing attention to yourself.","owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PZ7ttUGkz4mugl9l","name":"A long leather whip with metal studs and spikes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un largo látigo de cuero con tachuelas y pinchos metálicos","description":"<p>Un largo látigo de cuero con tachuelas y pinchos metálicos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A long leather whip with metal studs and spikes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sqvhbPswI7EO2FGs","name":"a beautiful fan to hide my face, dresses for every occasion","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un hermoso abanico tras el que ocultar el rostro","description":"<p>Un hermoso abanico tras el que ocultar el rostro</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a beautiful fan to hide my face, dresses for every occasion","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SSAfiLsWRWW8agap","name":"a long burgundy cape, gold and jewels gifted by countless suitors","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Vestidos para toda ocasión","description":"<p>Vestidos para toda ocasión</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a long burgundy cape, gold and jewels gifted by countless suitors","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OKYlFOmABR7C0JQ3","name":"a sharp stiletto I wear as a hairpin","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una larga capa de color burdeos","description":"<p>Una larga capa de color burdeos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a sharp stiletto I wear as a hairpin","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","quantity":1,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BNohnnLAsZdW76dA","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12","owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-regina-the-thief-of-hearts","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"12","contentKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Regina la Ladrona de Corazones","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Nací para ser líder y siempre me he rodeado de fieles seguidores dispuestos a satisfacer todos mis <br>caprichos. Al carecer del beneficio de la nobleza de nacimiento, el poder que ostentaba lo arreba -<br>taba de las manos de quienes menos merecían ejercerlo, sin importar el coste. Goberné ejércitos <br>de matones y rompí los corazones de hombres y mujeres. Tras cada conquista, partía en busca de <br>un desafío mayor. Como todavía hay mucho ahí fuera que debería ser mío por derecho, siempre <br>quiero más. La Orden me ha dado un nuevo propósito, una nueva perspectiva y nuevas criaturas <br>a las que esclavizar.<br>Tengo un encanto envidiable y me encanta arreglarme para encajar <br>en el papel que he elegido. Incluso cuando intento contenerme, nunca <br>paso desapercibida.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3XHmTgOnu0l2B2DI","name":"Babai the Judge","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/babai-el-juez.webp","items":[{"_id":"SoKNyzb5zMqYFiuA","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>PX<br>Soma<br> 6<br>Equipo<br>Un precioso y elegante vestido negro / Una capa y un <br>sombrero de copa / Un robusto bastón con una hoja <br>oculta / Un monóculo / Una Larva (máscara típica <br>del carnaval de Venecia) exquisitamente elaborada /<br>Un preciso reloj de bolsillo.<br>Heridas <br>1.<br>2.<br>3.<br>Herida <br>adicional.<br>Tras años de honorable servicio como inquisidor de estado de la República de Venecia, mi <br>cuerpo y mi espíritu han sufrido una rara mutación y ahora el miedo me es desconocido. La <br>gente siempre me ha llamado el hombre del saco, temiendo la justicia que representaba. Quizá <br>mi propia carencia de miedo me hacía aún más aterrador a los ojos de los mortales. La Orden <br>me ha encomendado una nueva misión porque, incluso en la lucha contra la oscuridad, alguien tiene que estar preparado para juzgar lo que está bien y lo que está mal.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"FIuZgXjddFAhDEk4","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender, evaluar y captar todos los detalles ocultos, razón por la que la Orden me quería como <br>juez. Soy frío, metódico y no soporto que los planes cambien <br>bruscamente.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9RlXXxhn8ePao4aj","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Mi cuerpo está hecho de pura sombra y puedo volverme <br>intangible durante breves instantes. Odio la luz del sol y no <br>puedo concentrarme bien cuando no estoy rodeado de una <br>sombra reconfortante.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L7O1ezrIll3E195s","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Mi presencia intimida a la gente, rozando el miedo que habita en lo <br>más profundo de su corazón. La presencia de los niños y su inocente <br>forma de ver el mundo me inquieta.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QBOzxGhLPTdMOX5u","name":"Eye of the Judge","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La mirada del juez","description":"<p>una vez por escena, cuando te encuentres con un grupo de PNJ entenderás inmediatamente quién <br>es el más y el menos capaz de ellos. Además, el Narrador también <br>te revelará si existen relaciones de amor, odio o fidelidad entre dos <br>PNJ de tu elección. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional cuando utilices la <br>información que has descubierto para intimidar o interrogar a <br>alguien.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when you meet a group of NPCs you will immediately understand who is the most and the least capable of them. Moreover, the Storyteller will also reveal to you if there are relationships such as love, hate, or fidelity between two NPCs of your choice. Receive 1 Additional Success when you use the information you have discovered to intimidate or question someone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bAWGlf21l1YlRfsv","name":"Like a Shadow","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Como una sombra","description":"<p>puedes gastar 1 Soma para manipular las sombras a tu favor, elige entre:<br>1. Te apropias de un objeto pequeño, aunque lo sostenga alguien, <br>siempre que puedas verlo<br>2. Haces que se caiga un objeto cercano.<br>3. Estira una sombra y manipula su forma para darle un aspecto <br>diferente.<br>Además, siempre obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba <br>de defensa que hagas mientras estés en una zona de sombra. Si <br>obtienes un triunfo, como efecto adicional puedes moverte de una <br>sombra a otra sin que nadie pueda impedírtelo.<br>Babai<br>el Juez</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to manipulate the shadows to your advantage, choose from:\n1. Acquire a small object, even if it is held by someone, as long as you can see it.\n2. Make an object in your immediate vicinity topple down.\n3. Stretch a shadow and manipulate its shape to make it look different.\nAdditionally, you always receive 1 Additional Success on any Defense Check you make while in a shaded area. If you get a successful Outcome, as an additional effect you can move from one shadow to another and no one can prevent it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aXMTnmPBva3b1m6F","name":"Dark Ego - If you don’t Stop, I’ll Call the Bogeyman!","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - ¡Si no paras, llamaré al hombre del saco","description":"<p>eres como una sombra serpenteante capaz de desplazarse a cualquier sitio. <br>Durante una escena, puedes llegar a un lugar cubriendo cualquier distancia <br>y superando cualquier obstáculo si uno de tus aliados o un PNJ te llama por <br>tu nombre. Cuando manifiestes tu verdadera naturaleza, todos los que lo <br>presencien se asustarán y no actuarán contra ti a menos que los amenaces <br>primero. El Narrador puede pedirte una prueba de posición para asustar a <br>personajes especialmente poderosos. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas <br>las pruebas de defensa que hagas contra las acciones de alguien que esté <br>asustado.</p>","trigger":"entra o sal de una sombra manifestando tu verdadera naturaleza y asustando a alguien."}}}},"system":{"description":"You are like a sinuous shadow that can reach anywhere. During a Scene, you can arrive at a location by covering any distance and overcoming any obstacle if one of your allies or an NPC calls your name. When you manifest your true nature, everyone who witnesses it will be frightened and will not act against you unless you threaten them first. The Storyteller may ask you for a Position Check to frighten particularly powerful characters. Receive 1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks you make against the actions of someone who is now fearful.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Enter or leave a shadow by manifesting your true nature and scaring someone.","owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"36eWJOLz7xnyRQPM","name":"A precious elegant black dress","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un precioso y elegante vestido negro","description":"<p>Un precioso y elegante vestido negro</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A precious elegant black dress","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1jKEbrATyLP0be1T","name":"a cape and a top hat","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una capa y un sombrero de copa","description":"<p>Una capa y un sombrero de copa</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a cape and a top hat","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"L21r0ykRu84rR2M7","name":"a sturdy cane with a hidden blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un robusto bastón con una hoja oculta","description":"<p>Un robusto bastón con una hoja oculta</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a sturdy cane with a hidden blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IivoGD4kJL2vbplO","name":"a monocle lens","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un monóculo","description":"<p>Un monóculo</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a monocle lens","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TlmRQ9tB7bW2fqPN","name":"an exquisitely crafted Larva (typical mask of the Venice Carnival)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una Larva (máscara típica del carnaval de Venecia) exquisitamente elaborada","description":"<p>Una Larva (máscara típica del carnaval de Venecia) exquisitamente elaborada</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"an exquisitely crafted Larva (typical mask of the Venice Carnival)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qNoW43jF9s5uTG3R","name":"an accurate pocket watch","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un preciso reloj de bolsillo.","description":"<p>Un preciso reloj de bolsillo.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"an accurate pocket watch","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","quantity":1,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"30q5lxFqmDtJP5hy","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14","owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-babai-the-judge","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"14","contentKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Babai el Juez","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Babai el Juez","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>PX<br>Soma<br> 6<br>Equipo<br>Un precioso y elegante vestido negro / Una capa y un <br>sombrero de copa / Un robusto bastón con una hoja <br>oculta / Un monóculo / Una Larva (máscara típica <br>del carnaval de Venecia) exquisitamente elaborada /<br>Un preciso reloj de bolsillo.<br>Heridas <br>1.<br>2.<br>3.<br>Herida <br>adicional.<br>Tras años de honorable servicio como inquisidor de estado de la República de Venecia, mi <br>cuerpo y mi espíritu han sufrido una rara mutación y ahora el miedo me es desconocido. La <br>gente siempre me ha llamado el hombre del saco, temiendo la justicia que representaba. Quizá <br>mi propia carencia de miedo me hacía aún más aterrador a los ojos de los mortales. La Orden <br>me ha encomendado una nueva misión porque, incluso en la lucha contra la oscuridad, alguien tiene que estar preparado para juzgar lo que está bien y lo que está mal.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Babai the Judge","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"q60PkmUrmX07umsK","name":"The Woman from the Woods","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/la-dama-de-los-bosques.webp","items":[{"_id":"shuvUSV86jddAi4P","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>He perdido la memoria. Lo primero que recuerdo es a la Orden encontrándome, vagando por el <br>bosque desnuda y cubierta de sangre. Tengo una fuerza extraordinaria y un instinto salvaje, tanto <br>que cualquier sociedad civilizada debería encadenarme como a un monstruo. Sé que en mi pasado hay un pecado tan grande, que mi memoria no podría soportar su peso. Pero quiero recordar <br>y quizá sirviendo a la Orden pueda hacerlo. Tengo una debilidad natural por los niños y no soporto <br>ver cómo les hacen daño. La Orden me utiliza como arma en los asuntos más graves, cuando es <br>necesario actuar con decisión y demostrar que un Cazador es una fuerza a tener en cuenta.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MLzMtN038mhIemBa","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy increíblemente fuerte. A pesar de mi aspecto menudo, soy más <br>dura que el más robusto de los hombres. Me cuesta controlar mi <br>fuerza y a menudo acabo destrozando cosas sin querer.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sZjlIKBPJPoWB4ir","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>A veces manifiesto extrañas aptitudes, herencia de un pasado que <br>ya no recuerdo. Pero, cuando lo necesito, el mundo que me rodea <br>se amolda para protegerme y cobijarme. Odio salir a la luz y ser <br>el centro de atención.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"plMcB5kxDsa4ji8c","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>La Dama<br>de los Bosques<br>Me encanta la carne humana y puedo hacerme una idea de <br>las personas solo con mirarlas. Me atraen sin remedio quienes tienen un rasgo físico particular que estimula mi apetito, <br>como buen olor o piel aterciopelada.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BFu0Abboh5sASuQx","name":"The Woman from the Wood","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques","description":"<p>obtienes 1 Éxito adicional a <br>cualquier prueba de posición que requiera que recurras a tu fuerza. Si <br>eliminas a un ser vivo causándole una Herida, puedes hacerlo de una <br>forma extremadamente perturbadora. Cualquiera que lo presencie, <br>a discreción del Narrador, bajará su Nivel de Oposición en 1 para la <br>siguiente acción.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You receive 1 Additional Success to any Position Check that requires you to resort to your strength. If you eliminate a living being by causing a Wound, you can do it in an extremely disturbing way. Anyone who witnesses it, at the discretion of the Storyteller, will lower their Opposition Level by 1 for the next action.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"BUr2574x41pMu0si","name":"Home Sweet Home","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Hogar dulce hogar","description":"<p>puede gastar 1 Soma para recurrir a los <br>extraños poderes de la bruja que una vez fuiste. Cuando lo hagas, elige <br>uno de los siguientes efectos.<br>1. Crea un refugio para una persona, perfectamente camuflado en <br>el entorno. Es muy difícil descubrir este refugio, aunque los PNJ se <br>acerquen. A discreción del Narrador, puede efectuarse una prueba de <br>Defensa para ver si lo descubren.<br>2. Cambias una planta de forma. Puedes, por ejemplo, crear una escalera con las ramas de un árbol o tejer ramas para que actúen como <br>escudo.<br>3. Conviertes algo repugnante o podrido en comestible, dándole un <br>aspecto dulce y tentador. Cualquiera que consuma tu dulce golosina <br>recupera 1 Herida.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You can spend 1 Soma to draw on the strange powers of the witch you once were. When you do so, choose one of the following effects:\n1. Create a shelter for one person, perfectly camouflaged within the environment.\n2. Reshape a plant to create ladders, shields, or other simple structures.\n3. Make something disgusting/rotten edible and sweet, restoring 1 Wound to whoever eats it (except yourself).","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"TkRTHCVmZOal1SMf","name":"Dark Ego - Soft and Succulent Flesh","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - Carne blanda y suculenta","description":"<p>la verdad es que ansías la carne humana, especialmente cruda y tomada de gente <br>maligna. Cuando infliges una Herida mediante una acción violenta <br>a alguien que consideras maligno, y si consigues un triunfo con un <br>Incremento, puedes infligir 1 Herida adicional. Una vez por escena, <br>cuando consumes carne humana, recuperas 1 Herida y el Narrador <br>revelará algunos recuerdos de la víctima, dándote información contextualizada sobre lo que estás buscando.</p>","trigger":"manifiestas descaradamente tu deseo de devorar carne hu-mana, sin que te importen las consecuencias."}}}},"system":{"description":"The truth is that you crave human flesh, especially when raw and taken from evil people. When you inflict a Wound through violent action on someone you deem evil, and if you reach an Outcome with an Increment, you may inflict 1 additional Wound. Once per Scene when you consume human flesh, you recover 1 Wound and the Storyteller will reveal some memories of the victim, giving you contextualized information about what you are looking for.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Blatantly manifest your desire to devour human flesh, regardless of the consequences.","owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1vtgedVHLkC96L69","name":"A doll and a little wooden soldier — the only items I had with me when I was found. A worn-out gray travel dress stained with blood. A sharp butcher’s knife. A hair ribbon, gift from a Hunter of the Order. A cookbook filled with recipes for cakes and sweets","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una muñeca y un soldadito de madera, los únicos objetos que llevaba conmigo cuando me encontraron. No sé de dónde vienen, pero los guardo como un tesoro","description":"<p>Una muñeca y un soldadito de madera, los únicos objetos que llevaba conmigo cuando me encontraron. No sé de dónde vienen, pero los guardo como un tesoro</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A doll and a little wooden soldier — the only items I had with me when I was found. A worn-out gray travel dress stained with blood. A sharp butcher’s knife. A hair ribbon, gift from a Hunter of the Order. A cookbook filled with recipes for cakes and sweets","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ulmg1cSQyP9UOtuK","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16","owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-the-woman-from-the-woods","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"16","contentKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"La Dama de los Bosques","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"La Dama de los Bosques","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>He perdido la memoria. Lo primero que recuerdo es a la Orden encontrándome, vagando por el <br>bosque desnuda y cubierta de sangre. Tengo una fuerza extraordinaria y un instinto salvaje, tanto <br>que cualquier sociedad civilizada debería encadenarme como a un monstruo. Sé que en mi pasado hay un pecado tan grande, que mi memoria no podría soportar su peso. Pero quiero recordar <br>y quizá sirviendo a la Orden pueda hacerlo. Tengo una debilidad natural por los niños y no soporto <br>ver cómo les hacen daño. La Orden me utiliza como arma en los asuntos más graves, cuando es <br>necesario actuar con decisión y demostrar que un Cazador es una fuerza a tener en cuenta.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"The Woman from the Woods","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"za41IlvlHuITYDR1","name":"TheImmortal","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/el-inmortal.webp","items":[{"_id":"jISMZdV1lVDclFIY","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>S oy un hechicero que ha encontrado la clave de la inmortalidad. La larga vida no ha hecho más que <br>despertar mi apetito de poder y, en su búsqueda, me he manchado con todos los pecados. El secreto que <br>se oculta tras mi interminable existencia es que he escondido mi alma, separándola de mi cuerpo. Por <br>desgracia, la Orden encontró su escondite y ahora está retenida fuera de mi alcance en una iglesia fortificada, sin dejarme otra opción que someterme a sus órdenes. Culpable de mil y un crímenes, la Orden <br>exige que compense cada uno con mil y un actos de virtud. Según esos necios predicadores, me están <br>guiando por el camino de la redención. En realidad, la Orden me trata como a un sirviente, dándome solo <br>las tareas más ingratas, sabiendo que no puedo ser sometido por la muerte. Permanezco humilde y en <br>silencio, esperando el día en que descubra dónde han escondido mi alma. Entonces desataré mi venganza <br>y aniquilaré a todo el Papado...</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NNbXx6HnyuKUUBnj","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Poseo conocimientos y sabiduría extraídos de siglos de <br>existencia, que puedo evocar cuando es necesario. A <br>menudo me pierdo en los recuerdos de mis glorias pasadas, olvidándome del mundo que me rodea.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"oIFu1Kyh9ZZtEqpn","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Aunque odio admitirlo, con el tiempo he empezado a <br>sentir cierto placer al hacer buenas obras.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ygOXscNR8AF8jgbt","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Mi cuerpo no es más que una herramienta que puedo manipular a voluntad, mucho más allá de los límites humanos ordinarios. A pesar de mi aspecto viejo y demacrado, no siento ni fatiga ni dolor. Como los asuntos de la carne ya no me preocupan, valoro las cosas bellas y las obras de arte por encima de cualquier otra cosa.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"t6uNsH4GstK3psDb","name":"Memories of an Infinite Life","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Recuerdos de una vida infinita","description":"<p>has estado <br>vivo durante un tiempo indefinido y lo sabes casi todo. Una <br>vez por escena, puedes pedir información sobre el pasado <br>o sobre un tema o lugar concreto, que solo está disponible <br>para ti debido a tu larga historia. El Narrador te proporcionará detalles relevantes y útiles que pueden estar a tu alcance debido a tus experiencias. Una vez por escena, puedes <br>cambiar el descriptor asociado a este don (pero no la desventaja) por otro que represente una habilidad que hayas <br>conjurado en tu mente inmortal. Este nuevo descriptor es <br>tuyo hasta el final de la escena y obtienes 1 Éxito adicional <br>la primera vez que lo uses para una prueba.<br>La Orden utiliza mis poderes para sus propios fines <br>y, como resultado, he tenido que volverme hábil para <br>comprender y apoyar las necesidades de mis aliados.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You have been alive for an indefinite time and know almost everything. Once per Scene, you may ask for information about the past or a specific subject or place, which is only available to you due to your long history. The Storyteller will provide relevant and useful details. Once per Scene, you may also change the above Descriptor associated with this Gift to one that represents a skill you have conjured to your immortal mind. This new Descriptor is yours until the end of the Scene, and you receive 1 Additional Success the first time you use it for a Check.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Xs9kKLGeRYIgV1z6","name":"The Servant","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El sirviente","description":"<p>una vez por escena, como acción adicional, puedes conceder 1 Éxito adicional a la acción de un <br>aliado si puedes apoyarlo narrativamente. Además, siempre <br>puedes gastar Soma para pagar el coste de activación de los <br>dones de tus aliados.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, as an additional action, you can grant 1 Additional Success to an ally’s action if you can narratively support them. You can also always spend your Soma to pay the activation cost of your allies’ Gifts.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GKhCJlMmyOAwFbem","name":"Dark Ego - The Immortal","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - El Inmortal","description":"<p>cuando sufres 1 Herida, puedes gastar inmediatamente 1 Soma para permanecer consciente, lo que te permite sufrir muchas</p>","trigger":""}}}},"system":{"description":"When you suffer 1 Wound, you can immediately spend 1 Soma to remain conscious, allowing you to suffer many Wounds without dying. You are in full control of your body, even parts that have been cut off. You can see through a torn eye or continue to use your severed hand. At the end of the Scene in which you activated your Dark Ego, you recover all Wounds suffered except the first one. Your body regenerates and severed parts reattach in a horrific spectacle.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Use your indifference to pain or death to your advantage, revealing your true nature for anyone to see.","owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zWTNeERIGRtzpnwK","name":"Poor clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ropa pobre","description":"<p>Ropa pobre</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Poor clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WhySEJnnDD0UlG1L","name":"a worn out sickle (reminder of times past)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una hoz gastada, recuerdo de tiempos pasados","description":"<p>Una hoz gastada, recuerdo de tiempos pasados</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a worn out sickle (reminder of times past)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qnPcACLkwGsZ1yD9","name":"a small bag with precious items collected during adventures","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una pequeña bolsa con algunos objetos preciosos que has recogido en tus aventuras","description":"<p>Una pequeña bolsa con algunos objetos preciosos que has recogido en tus aventuras</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a small bag with precious items collected during adventures","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"y5674t6cMw1HPEZG","name":"a key that opens one of many secret refuges","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una llave que abre la puerta de uno de tus muchos refugios secretos","description":"<p>Una llave que abre la puerta de uno de tus muchos refugios secretos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a key that opens one of many secret refuges","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vp2zZtUn94CbnFlj","name":"a papal ring as a symbol of indenture to the Church","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un anillo papal, símbolo de tu compromiso con la Iglesia","description":"<p>Un anillo papal, símbolo de tu compromiso con la Iglesia</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a papal ring as a symbol of indenture to the Church","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"b2kejfRXpUdubEwb","name":"a little toy given by someone helped with the first good deed","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un pequeño juguete, que te regaló quien ayudaste con tu primera buena acción.","description":"<p>Un pequeño juguete, que te regaló quien ayudaste con tu primera buena acción.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a little toy given by someone helped with the first good deed","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","quantity":1,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4fTfPjQFfu9zpAmE","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18","owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-theimmortal","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"18","contentKey":"cazador.theimmortal","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"El Inmortal","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"El Inmortal","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>S oy un hechicero que ha encontrado la clave de la inmortalidad. La larga vida no ha hecho más que <br>despertar mi apetito de poder y, en su búsqueda, me he manchado con todos los pecados. El secreto que <br>se oculta tras mi interminable existencia es que he escondido mi alma, separándola de mi cuerpo. Por <br>desgracia, la Orden encontró su escondite y ahora está retenida fuera de mi alcance en una iglesia fortificada, sin dejarme otra opción que someterme a sus órdenes. Culpable de mil y un crímenes, la Orden <br>exige que compense cada uno con mil y un actos de virtud. Según esos necios predicadores, me están <br>guiando por el camino de la redención. En realidad, la Orden me trata como a un sirviente, dándome solo <br>las tareas más ingratas, sabiendo que no puedo ser sometido por la muerte. Permanezco humilde y en <br>silencio, esperando el día en que descubra dónde han escondido mi alma. Entonces desataré mi venganza <br>y aniquilaré a todo el Papado...</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"TheImmortal","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy..."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":7,"max":7},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"kyL3B6saQzGIVmt4","name":"Marina the Sea Explorer","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/marina-la-exploradora-del-mar.webp","items":[{"_id":"ZVRIUMALsQ5LZksI","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Soy una viajera y, a lo largo de los años, he visitado todos los lugares conocidos por el hombre. <br>Ser una mercader ambulante me ha permitido ocultar fácilmente de miradas indiscretas mi talento como bruja. Año tras año, he acumulado todo tipo de riquezas mágicas y mundanas. Pero <br>la Orden me encontró y me obligó a firmar el contrato más unilateral de toda mi carrera como <br>comerciante. Ahora debo poner mis habilidades y mi carisma al servicio de la Orden, intentando <br>ganar lo máximo posible para redimir la enorme deuda que me han hecho contraer con engaños.<br>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy <br>tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"u6wEMSSvu2Dswkjb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy una bruja del mar y, como tal, tengo el poder de moldear <br>el agua y moverla a voluntad. Odio los lugares cerrados, aislados de la presencia de mi amado mar.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sR0shGRyDLFeDv61","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Nadie conoce mi verdadera forma, que oculto bajo una apariencia de eterna juventud. Puedo cambiar de forma hasta <br>cierto punto, sin dejar de ser humana. Me atraen irremediablemente todas las formas de belleza y a menudo me pierdo en <br>su contemplación.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2hZ4nkOQm1FMczAH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy <br>tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GupGFKV1FnbEWxe9","name":"Sea Magic","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Magia del mar","description":"<p>puedes dar rienda suelta a tus poderes de <br>bruja y controlar el agua de mar, manipulándola como si fuera sólida. Puedes utilizarla como arma o como objeto para respaldar tus <br>acciones, dándole la consistencia de un látigo que puede alcanzar <br>hasta 9 metros. Cuando actúas, puedes realizar una segunda acción de apoyo, como recoger algo, mover a alguien a quien quieras <br>defender o dificultar el movimiento de un enemigo gracias al agua <br>que manipulas. También puedes utilizar este don con agua dulce, <br>pero para ello tendrás que gastar 1 Soma.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You can unleash your witch powers and control seawater, manipulating it as if it were solid. You can use it as a weapon or as an object to support your actions, giving it the consistency of a whip that can reach up to thirty feet. When you act, you can take a second supporting action, such as picking up something, moving someone you want to defend, or hindering an enemy’s movement thanks to the water you manipulate. You can also use this Gift with fresh water, but you will need to spend 1 Soma to do so.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3XBPXukzSpq7ztTN","name":"Mutable Appearance","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Apariencia mutable","description":"<p>puedes cambiar tu apariencia una <br>vez por escena. Crea un descriptor que represente tu nuevo aspecto. Nadie puede traspasar tu engaño, excepto a través de medios mágicos o dones que permitan descubrir la verdad. Además, <br>puedes gastar 1 Soma para adoptar la apariencia específica de una <br>persona a la que ya hayas conocido, imitando también su voz y sus <br>modales. Puedes mantener tu nueva apariencia hasta que termine <br>la escena.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene you can change your appearance. Create a Descriptor that represents your new appearance. Nobody can pierce your deception, except through magical means or Gifts that allow one to discover the truth. In addition, you may spend 1 Soma to take the specific appearance of a person you have already met, mimicking their voice and manners as well. You can keep your new appearance until the Scene is over.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QeEN1jC9jmbiDIWF","name":"Dark Ego - Treasures of the Sea","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – Tesoros del mar","description":"<p>al principio del escenario, <br>obtienes 2 Contadores de tesoro. Cuando muestres tus tesoros, gasta <br>1 Contador de tesoro y 1 Soma, y crea un descriptor que lo represente, como por ejemplo Daga matalobos o Lente de la verdad . Obtén 1 <br>Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba en la que tu tesoro pueda ser útil. <br>Alternativamente, gasta 1 Contador para sacar una Poción de tu bolsa <br>y dársela a alguien. Crea un descriptor para representar su efecto mágico, por ejemplo Ver en la oscuridad o Fuerza extraordinaria. Quien la <br>beba obtendrá el descriptor que has creado durante 1 escena, más 1 Éxito <br>adicional en la primera acción en la que utilice la ventaja otorgada por la <br>poción. Cuando obtengas un nuevo tesoro o cierres un trato favorable, <br>recibirás 1 Contador de tesoro.</p>","trigger":"convertir una petición de ayuda o una conversación en una \nnegociación, dejando claro lo increíbles que son tus tesoros."}}}},"system":{"description":"At the beginning of the Scenario, you receive 2 Treasure Tokens. When you show off your Treasures, spend 1 Treasure Token and 1 Soma, and create a Descriptor that represents it such as Wolf-Slaying Dagger or Lens of Truth. Receive 1 Additional Success for any Check in which your Treasure may be helpful. Alternatively, spend 1 Token to draw a Potion from your pouch to give to someone. Create a Descriptor to represent its magical effect such as Seeing in the dark or Extraordinary strength. Whoever drinks it will be granted the Descriptor you created for 1 Scene, plus 1 Additional Success on the first action in which they use the advantage given by the potion. When you obtain a new treasure or close a favorable deal, you receive 1 Treasure Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Turn a request for help or a conversation into a negotiation, making it clear how amazing your treasures are.","owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"qApqG6IWXBrTdqw6","name":"Exotic and colorful dresses","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Vestidos exóticos y coloridos","description":"<p>Vestidos exóticos y coloridos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Exotic and colorful dresses","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CP6qvHLrZsQJkiPz","name":"a large bag full of treasures","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una bolsa grande llena de tesoros","description":"<p>Una bolsa grande llena de tesoros</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a large bag full of treasures","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Emjm9UAFYAHqzL6O","name":"a travel bag","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una bolsa de viaje","description":"<p>Una bolsa de viaje</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a travel bag","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"W1mP65fQXaYQan5V","name":"rings and fine jewelry made out of seashells","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Anillos y joyas refinadas de conchas marinas","description":"<p>Anillos y joyas refinadas de conchas marinas</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"rings and fine jewelry made out of seashells","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"7pjPiemNDABvGPvA","name":"a vial of sea water","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un frasco de agua de mar","description":"<p>Un frasco de agua de mar</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a vial of sea water","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2a7b7h7Qx0WCdynr","name":"cosmetics and perfumes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Cosméticos y perfumes.","description":"<p>Cosméticos y perfumes.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"cosmetics and perfumes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","quantity":1,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"o1iukLILymozhmC3","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20","owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-marina-the-sea-explorer","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"20","contentKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Marina la Exploradora del Mar","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Soy una viajera y, a lo largo de los años, he visitado todos los lugares conocidos por el hombre. <br>Ser una mercader ambulante me ha permitido ocultar fácilmente de miradas indiscretas mi talento como bruja. Año tras año, he acumulado todo tipo de riquezas mágicas y mundanas. Pero <br>la Orden me encontró y me obligó a firmar el contrato más unilateral de toda mi carrera como <br>comerciante. Ahora debo poner mis habilidades y mi carisma al servicio de la Orden, intentando <br>ganar lo máximo posible para redimir la enorme deuda que me han hecho contraer con engaños.<br>Tengo una enorme colección de reliquias y tesoros mágicos. Soy muy <br>tacaña con mi colección y busco constantemente aumentar mi riqueza para poder recuperar mi libertad.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Marina the Sea Explorer","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"whJgabNRDwMRmcLY","name":"Niklaus von Krampus","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/niklaus-von-krampus.webp","items":[{"_id":"04xhCrcrobixW4N6","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>S oy un clérigo devoto que siempre ha dedicado su vida a ayudar a los demás. Con los años me he con<br>-vertido en un exorcista de talento y esta vocación mía me llevó al remoto pueblo de Borgo Maleanime. Allí <br>luché contra un demonio especialmente insidioso, que se ocultaba entre las filas de una pandilla de jóvenes <br>matones que solo fingían ser demonios para asustar a la gente. Fue un combate duro, pero finalmente con<br>-seguí vencer al demonio. O eso creía. Algo en el exorcismo no salió como esperaba y ahora el demonio habita <br>en mi interior, sembrando el miedo y el dolor cada vez que reaparece. La Orden me acogió en sus filas como <br>exorcista y acepté de buen grado este papel, con la esperanza de que las misiones que me encomendaran me <br>permitieran encontrar la forma de librarme, de una vez por todas, de aquello que se esconde en mi interior.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"l68E99pdP9DGenIw","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy un experto exorcista. Sé identificar y combatir el mal <br>mediante la oración y las artes sagradas. A pesar de lo <br>que soy, odio los lugares sagrados y las manifestaciones <br>de fe y religión, ya que hacen que se agite el demonio que <br>llevo dentro.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ci9rCgfmvvzwAd8f","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Se me da bien comprender a la gente y ayudarla. Ahora, <br>gracias al demonio que habita en mí, puedo incluso percibir el lado oscuro de las personas. Sin embargo, de vez <br>en cuando, el demonio se apodera de mí y me hace comportarme de forma extraña ante la gente corriente.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Ivh0kypSdWvqLsHX","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>El demonio que hay en mí me otorga su poder, permitiéndome actuar con <br>una fuerza y velocidad salvajes. No es fácil contener esta ferocidad y, a menudo, acabo hiriendo a alguien o destrozando cosas cuando no era mi intención.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JESolgVFAmNDTg27","name":"Exorcist","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Exorcista","description":"<p>cuando te enfrentas a un ser claramente sobrenatural, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en todas las pruebas. También <br>puedes invocar rituales sagrados y plegarias para perturbar el <br>mal al que te enfrentas. Si un sujeto, artefacto o manifestación <br>sobrenatural utiliza un don que conoces o ya has visto en acción, <br>puedes gastar 1 Soma para impedir su uso. Cada vez que actives <br>este don, tira 1 dado. Si sacas un 5 o un 6, obtienes 1 Contador <br>de diablo.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"When you face a clearly supernatural being, you gain 1 Additional Success on all Checks. You can also invoke sacred rites and prayers to disturb the evil you face. If a subject, artifact, or supernatural manifestation uses a Gift that you know of or have already seen in action, you can spend 1 Soma to prevent its use. Each time you activate this Gift, roll 1 die. If you roll a 5 or a 6, you gain 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vsgjj5DC3hqkKe4d","name":"The Inner Demon","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El demonio interior","description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes liberar al demonio interior, ya sea tuyo o de otra persona. En tu <br>caso, crea un descriptor que represente una emoción que incluya <br>la palabra Ira, Envidia o Perversidad. Obtienes 2 Éxitos adicionales la primera vez que usas este descriptor para una prueba <br>de posición. Si desatas el demonio interior de otra persona, el <br>Narrador creará un descriptor para ella que muestre su lado oscuro oculto. Cuando utilices este don con personas especialmente poderosas, el Narrador puede pedirte que realices una prueba <br>de posición para tener éxito. Cada vez que uses este don, recibirás 1 Contador de diablo.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can release the inner demon, whether that’d be yours or someone else’s. In your case, create a Descriptor that represents an emotion that includes the word Anger, Envy, or Wickedness. You receive 2 Additional Successes the first time you use this Descriptor for a Position Check. If you unleash someone else’s inner demon, the Storyteller will create a Descriptor for them that showcases their hidden, dark side. When using this Gift on particularly powerful individuals, the Storyteller may request a Position Check from you to succeed. Each time you use this Gift, you receive 1 Devil Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"a63uL08VSdNWLXaT","name":"Dark Ego - The Demon Revealed","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – El demonio revelado","description":"<p>aunque generalmente mantienes <br>el control, de vez en cuando tienes que permitir que el demonio se manifieste y <br>desate su ira. Crea un descriptor que represente tu forma demoníaca y que incluya <br>al menos una de estas palabras: Monstruoso, Feroz, Bestial. Tus características físicas van mucho más allá de las de un simple mortal, pero te comportarás como un <br>demonio, disfrutando de la maldad y el miedo que inspiras. Cuando actúas usando <br>este descriptor especial, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional. Puedes gastar 1 Contador de <br>diablo para infligir 1 Herida adicional o para gastar como Soma en una prueba. <br>Una vez por escenario, el Narrador puede usar 1 Contador de diablo para activar <br>este don contra tu voluntad.</p>","trigger":"dar rienda suelta a tu lado demoníaco o escuchar el sonido de campanas \no cencerros durante al menos un minuto."}}}},"system":{"description":"While generally retaining control, every now and then you have to allow the demon to manifest and unleash its anger. Create a Descriptor that represents your demonic form and that includes at least one of these words: Monstrous, Fierce, Beastly. Your physical abilities go far beyond those of a mere mortal, but you will behave like a devil, enjoying the evil and fear you inspire. When you act using this special Descriptor, you gain 1 Additional Success. You can spend 1 Devil Token to inflict 1 additional Wound or to spend as Soma for a Check. Once per Scenario, the Storyteller can spend 1 Devil Token to activate this Gift against your will.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Give free rein to your demonic side or listen to the sound of bells or cowbells for at least one minute.","owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gRV9d3yi4TT6JP1D","name":"An old cassock worn from many travels","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una vieja sotana, desgastada por muchos viajes","description":"<p>Una vieja sotana, desgastada por muchos viajes</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"An old cassock worn from many travels","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"u790puWrJRxlhH0h","name":"exorcism vestments and tools","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ornamentos y herramientas de exorcismo","description":"<p>Ornamentos y herramientas de exorcismo</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"exorcism vestments and tools","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YItt8eU1d5R04JjU","name":"a shepherd’s curved staff of wood and iron to beat the devil with","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una vieja bolsa donde se encuentran cosas que el demonio toma cuando está en control (a menudo, con un origen poco claro que no quieres saber)","description":"<p>Una vieja bolsa donde se encuentran cosas que el demonio toma cuando está en control (a menudo, con un origen poco claro que no quieres saber)</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a shepherd’s curved staff of wood and iron to beat the devil with","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GHMwTBl5tqX8WmLd","name":"an old pouch containing mysterious items taken while the demon is in control","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un cayado curvo de pastor de madera y hierro para golpear al demonio","description":"<p>Un cayado curvo de pastor de madera y hierro para golpear al demonio</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"an old pouch containing mysterious items taken while the demon is in control","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"sxypMupsoc6WoQ0t","name":"precious small relics received as offerings","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Reliquias preciosas y pequeñas recibidas como ofrendas","description":"<p>Reliquias preciosas y pequeñas recibidas como ofrendas</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"precious small relics received as offerings","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"oM4cu0m0JPS3K0H0","name":"an old, time-worn bible","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una biblia vieja y desgastada por el tiempo.","description":"<p>Una biblia vieja y desgastada por el tiempo.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"an old, time-worn bible","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","quantity":1,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Aky98Vk4vWloSldL","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22","owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-niklaus-von-krampus","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"22","contentKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Niklaus von Krampus","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Niklaus von Krampus","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>S oy un clérigo devoto que siempre ha dedicado su vida a ayudar a los demás. Con los años me he con<br>-vertido en un exorcista de talento y esta vocación mía me llevó al remoto pueblo de Borgo Maleanime. Allí <br>luché contra un demonio especialmente insidioso, que se ocultaba entre las filas de una pandilla de jóvenes <br>matones que solo fingían ser demonios para asustar a la gente. Fue un combate duro, pero finalmente con<br>-seguí vencer al demonio. O eso creía. Algo en el exorcismo no salió como esperaba y ahora el demonio habita <br>en mi interior, sembrando el miedo y el dolor cada vez que reaparece. La Orden me acogió en sus filas como <br>exorcista y acepté de buen grado este papel, con la esperanza de que las misiones que me encomendaran me <br>permitieran encontrar la forma de librarme, de una vez por todas, de aquello que se esconde en mi interior.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Niklaus von Krampus","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xblP0GvPJ1k5RXPU","name":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/san-jorge-el-matadragones.webp","items":[{"_id":"wXG4Ju1hwoYVfMK0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>No hay piedad para los monstruos, ni perdón para los que se unen y sirven a las fuerzas del mal.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4OCrrV26B9D4ADio","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>He dedicado mi vida a matar monstruos y aberraciones, perfeccionando mi cuerpo y mi habilidad para ello. <br>Mi estricta disciplina hace que rara vez me sienta inclinado a perdonar los errores de los demás.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8tq5ea631EDCulS0","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>He jurado erradicar todo el mal de este mundo y nada <br>puede escapar a mi mirada inquisitiva. Odio todos los <br>secretos, pues sé que la semilla del mal puede crecer dentro de cualquiera.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"iIq0cXGarCpvOfjx","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>San Jorge <br>el matadragones<br>Soy un santo a los ojos de la gente corriente y ninguna puerta per -<br>manece cerrada para mí. Mi palabra es la de la propia Iglesia. Lo que <br>digo no se pone en duda.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HXE5OfVfw2uzW8Zq","name":"The Dragon Slayer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"El matadragones","description":"<p>eres experto en matar monstruos y criaturas demoníacas en nombre de la fe. Empiezas <br>cada escenario con 1 Contador de fervor. Cuando te enfrentas <br>a un enemigo que es obviamente monstruoso, si obtienes un <br>triunfo en una prueba de posición, puedes usar 1 Contador de <br>fervor para infligir 1 herida adicional. Cuando un enemigo de <br>este tipo intente abrumarte usando uno de sus dones, puedes <br>usar 1 Contador de fervor para obtener 2 éxitos adicionales <br>en tu prueba de defensa. Cuando sufres 1 Herida, obtienes 1 <br>Contador de fervor.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You’re skilled at slaying monsters and demonic creatures in the name of faith. You start each Scenario with 1 Fervor Token. When facing an enemy that is obviously monstrous, if you get a successful Outcome on a Position Check, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to inflict 1 additional Wound. When such an enemy attempts to overwhelm you using one of their Gifts, you can spend 1 Fervor Token to receive 2 Additional Successes to your Defense Check. When you suffer 1 Wound, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XBqPD0AKBG7e8ciT","name":"Agent of the Papacy","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Agente del papado","description":"<p>cuando hablas a una multitud <br>puedes infundir en su corazón la luz de la fe. Usa 1 Contador <br>de fervor y crea un descriptor que represente un sentimiento <br>de fe, ira y deseo de justicia contra el mal. Como alternati -<br>va, crea un descriptor que represente confianza y sumisión <br>en dicha fe. La multitud actuará en consecuencia durante <br>el resto de la escena, pero los PNJ especialmente poderosos <br>pueden ser inmunes a tus palabras. Obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier prueba que hagas usando el sentimiento que <br>inspiraste. Cuando expones públicamente el mal, obtienes 1 <br>Contador de fervor.<br>Soy el agente más hábil y de mayor confianza del Papado y, como tal, es mi responsabilidad <br>asegurarme de que la lucha contra la oscuridad nunca decaiga. De niño, me caí a un río y casi <br>me ahogo, pero me salvó una criatura que más tarde descubrí que era un dragón. Cuando crecí, <br>hice los votos sagrados y me uní a la Iglesia. Al hacerlo, descubrí que el que creía mi salvador <br>era en realidad una criatura de las tinieblas, dispuesta a robarme el alma. Juré luchar contra <br>las tinieblas, reprimiendo el sentimiento de gratitud hacia el dragón que me salvó, que siempre <br>me ha atormentado. Semejante debilidad representa una grieta por la que podría colarse el mal.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"When you speak to a crowd you can infuse their hearts with the light of faith. Spend 1 Fervor Token and you can create a Descriptor that represents a feeling of faith, anger, and a desire for justice against evil. Alternatively, create a Descriptor that represents trust and submission in such faith. The crowd will act accordingly for the rest of the Scene, but particularly powerful NPCs may be immune to your words. Receive 1 Additional Success on any Check you make using the sentiment you inspired. When you publicly expose evil, you receive 1 Fervor Token.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"XepUdrzCabSwj2Q1","name":"Dark Ego - The Saint","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – El santo","description":"<p>cuando canalizas el poder divino sagrado, <br>todo el mundo inclina la cabeza. La gente corriente te muestra reverencia, <br>mientras que los PNJ enemigos más débiles (a discreción del Narrador) no <br>te atacan a menos que seas la única opción disponible, ni intentan inter -<br>ponerse en tu camino. En tu presencia, cualquiera que tenga poderes relacionados con lo sobrenatural reduce su Nivel de Oposición en 1. Tu aura <br>sagrada emite una luz intensa que puede iluminar toda la zona que te rodea <br>a tu voluntad.</p>","trigger":"invocar el santo poder divino, reprendiendo a todos los pecadores y \ndando ejemplo de pureza y rectitud."}}}},"system":{"description":"When you channel sacred divine power, everyone bows their heads. Ordinary people will show you reverence, while weaker enemy NPCs (at the Storyteller’s discretion) won’t target you unless you’re the only available option, nor will they try to get in your way. In your presence, anyone possessing powers linked to the supernatural lowers their Opposition Level by 1. Your holy aura emits an intense light that can illuminate the whole area around you at your will.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Invoke holy divine power by reproaching all sinners and providing an example of purity and righteousness.","owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OuoavVWxMG4CLdeh","name":"Sacred armor","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Mi armadura sagrada","description":"<p>Mi armadura sagrada</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Sacred armor","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"doKRv9DGaEmOjdT3","name":"a sword and a spear blessed by the Pope himself","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una espada y una lanza bendecidas por el propio Papa","description":"<p>Una espada y una lanza bendecidas por el propio Papa</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a sword and a spear blessed by the Pope himself","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JVCVcor3TbZkmSdn","name":"my proud war stallion","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Mi orgulloso destrero","description":"<p>Mi orgulloso destrero</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"my proud war stallion","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"g2YzM3apaDGSLWt9","name":"a cross engraved with the Keys of Saint Peter (universal symbol of power)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una cruz con las Llaves de San Pedro grabadas, como símbolo universal de poder","description":"<p>Una cruz con las Llaves de San Pedro grabadas, como símbolo universal de poder</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a cross engraved with the Keys of Saint Peter (universal symbol of power)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OIcFCwNKdK7DBdeG","name":"Aldebrand the faithful squire","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Aldebrand, mi fiel escudero y sirviente","description":"<p>Aldebrand, mi fiel escudero y sirviente</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Aldebrand the faithful squire","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"48shOV04o3cwCVHg","name":"papal papers and seals","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Papeles y sellos papales","description":"<p>Papeles y sellos papales</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"papal papers and seals","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"YOnIYrMdDOdv31Yd","name":"a cloak of fine workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"equipment","sequence":7,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una capa de fina factura.","description":"<p>Una capa de fina factura.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a cloak of fine workmanship","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","quantity":1,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"z3fo41Qlg60ukEmi","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24","owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"24","contentKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"San Jorge el Matadragones","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"San Jorge el Matadragones","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>No hay piedad para los monstruos, ni perdón para los que se unen y sirven a las fuerzas del mal.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"TgakOPCFRsrxj12j","name":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/sun-wukong-el-mono-asombroso.webp","items":[{"_id":"yZXguvum1zHM800T","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Sun Wukong<br>el Mono Asombroso</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"40PqdB4fqPHs3Hrb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy un guardián experto. Mi cuerpo es fuerte y robusto, mis <br>sentidos agudos y alerta. Años de cautiverio me han vuelto <br>sumiso, y lucho por no seguir todas las órdenes que me dan.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"G5DOeLCqb9BvDhqp","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Soy más fuerte y más rápido que cualquier humano y soy <br>un luchador muy hábil. No rehúyo los retos porque siempre <br>creo que puedo ganar.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9TWPKlV3psYnuThW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p></p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KlMwH9gpLtgIB4CI","name":"Guardian Disciple","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Discípulo guardián","description":"<p>puedes interceptar un peligro antes <br>de que abrume a tu aliado. Puedes gastar 1 Soma para interponerte entre un aliado y un peligro poniéndote en su lugar. Obtienes <br>1 Éxito adicional a cualquier prueba de defensa que tengas que <br>llevar a cabo en la acción. Una vez por escenario, puedes ignorar <br>1 Herida que sufras.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You can intercept a danger before it overwhelms your ally. You may spend 1 Soma to get between an ally and a danger by standing in their place. Receive 1 Additional Success to any Defense Check you have to perform doing so. Once per Scenario, you can ignore 1 Wound you suffer.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aoeKxojpd0bau9hM","name":"Monkey King","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Rey mono","description":"<p>eres capaz de realizar proezas atléticas impensables para un simple mortal. Puedes gastar 1 Soma y elegir un <br>efecto:<br>1. Puedes saltar increíblemente lejos, hasta 9 metros. Además, <br>eres capaz de cargar a otra persona sobre tus hombros. También <br>ignoras cualquier daño relacionado con una caída.<br>2. Usar la cola para manipular un objeto y realizar una acción <br>adicional.<br>3. Ignorar cualquier impedimento físico para el movimiento utilizando tus impresionantes habilidades.<br>No tengo recuerdos de mi vida anterior a mi cautiverio, aunque a menudo sueño con los bosques y las cumbres nevadas de mi querida China. Crecí como un animal de circo en el Royal <br>Circus de Londres, pero, en lo más profundo de mi ser, tengo la convicción de que estoy destinado a algo más. Me rebelé matando a todos mis captores, huyendo a través de una vasta <br>y laberíntica ciudad. Cuando la Orden me alcanzó, pensé que era el fin, pero los Cazadores me <br>llevaron con ellos como su guardián y defensor. Cuanto más vivo como Cazador, más me acerco <br>a la trascendencia. Ahora soy consciente de que, algún día, descubriré quién soy en realidad.<br>Mi esencia es mágica, y esto me hace resistente a los encantamientos que <br>podrían apresar a los estúpidos humanos. Mi presencia espiritual es imponente, y me cuesta ocultar lo que soy, sobre todo a los ojos de quienes están <br>acostumbrados a la magia.<br>• Ego oscuro - Descendiente del Despertar del Vacío y la <br>Vacuidad: cuando liberas tu verdadero poder, tu cuerpo emite una luz <br>divina y nadie puede detenerte. Puedes sufrir 1 Herida adicional para obtener <br>2 Éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba física que tengas que realizar. Durante <br>el resto de la escena, los hechizos tienen poco efecto sobre ti y obtienes 2 <br>éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba de defensa que realices para protegerte <br>de los efectos arcanos. Cuando golpeas a alguien, puedes gastar 1 Soma para <br>infligirle 1 Herida adicional. Los efectos de este don terminan si te comportas <br>de forma serena y obediente, como dicta tu papel de guardián.<br>Activador: Actuar con pasión y fuerza, mostrando a todo el mundo el increíble poder que encierra tu cuerpo.<br>Equipo <br>Un palo de circo con tres segmentos que puedo extender / <br>Ropa de circo vieja y gastada / Una vieja diadema dorada <br>tan ajustada a mi frente que no se puede quitar / Una sábana con el dibujo de un paisaje chino, regalo de un niño que <br>vio uno de mis espectáculos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"You are able to perform athletic feats unthinkable to a mere mortal. You may spend 1 Soma and choose an effect:\n1. You can jump incredibly far, up to thirty feet. You can bring another person with you by carrying them on your shoulders. You also ignore any damage related to a fall.\n2. Use your tail to manipulate an object and perform an additional action.\n3. Ignore any physical impediments to movement by using your impressive skills.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lTFcCRItqRACFeR5","name":"Dark Ego - Descendant of the Awakening of the Void and the Emptiness","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - Descendiente del Despertar del Vacío y la Vacuidad","description":"<p>cuando liberas tu verdadero poder, tu cuerpo emite una luz <br>divina y nadie puede detenerte. Puedes sufrir 1 Herida adicional para obtener <br>2 Éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba física que tengas que realizar. Durante <br>el resto de la escena, los hechizos tienen poco efecto sobre ti y obtienes 2 <br>éxitos adicionales a cualquier prueba de defensa que realices para protegerte <br>de los efectos arcanos. Cuando golpeas a alguien, puedes gastar 1 Soma para <br>infligirle 1 Herida adicional. Los efectos de este don terminan si te comportas <br>de forma serena y obediente, como dicta tu papel de guardián.</p>","trigger":"Actuar con pasión y fuerza, mostrando a todo el mundo el increíble poder que encierra tu cuerpo."}}}},"system":{"description":"When you release your true power, your body emits a divine light and no one can stop you. Take 1 Wound to get 2 Additional Successes to any physical Checks you have to perform. For the rest of the Scene spells have little effect on you and you get 2 Additional Successes to any Defense Check you make to protect yourself from arcane effects. When you deal a hit to someone, you can spend 1 Soma to inflict 1 additional Wound. The effects of this Gift cease if you behave in a composed and obedient manner, as your role as guardian dictates.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Act with passion and strength, showing everyone the incredible power that lies within your body.","owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QNNmgIwxvfuOVyBc","name":"A circus stick with three extendable segments","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un palo de circo con tres segmentos que puedo extender","description":"<p>Un palo de circo con tres segmentos que puedo extender</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A circus stick with three extendable segments","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2wPnGzfhE8TEqUJy","name":"old and worn circus clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ropa de circo vieja y gastada","description":"<p>Ropa de circo vieja y gastada</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"old and worn circus clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vznDDlwxi25Ktrzp","name":"a golden diadem so tight on my forehead that it cannot be removed","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una vieja diadema dorada tan ajustada a mi frente que no se puede quitar","description":"<p>Una vieja diadema dorada tan ajustada a mi frente que no se puede quitar</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a golden diadem so tight on my forehead that it cannot be removed","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"aWNyPFQVAZZ9vJ7B","name":"a sheet with the drawing of a Chinese landscape — gift from a child who once watched one of my shows","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una sábana con el dibujo de un paisaje chino, regalo de un niño que vio uno de mis espectáculos.","description":"<p>Una sábana con el dibujo de un paisaje chino, regalo de un niño que vio uno de mis espectáculos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a sheet with the drawing of a Chinese landscape — gift from a child who once watched one of my shows","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","quantity":1,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EOgymLZjvOkFCbVl","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26","owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"26","contentKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Sun Wukong el Mono Asombroso","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Sun Wukong<br>el Mono Asombroso</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZtqN5q5NZ6u5KWFJ","name":"Verdoux Bluebeard","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/verdoux-barba-azul.webp","items":[{"_id":"vNF86xgicyxSrM6h","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>Soy un aristócrata francés, al que mi soberano llama para gestionar los asuntos más retorcidos y de peor reputación. He vivido una vida poco convencional, entre la realización de tareas imposibles y el mantenimiento <br>de secretos inconfesables, que me ha abierto los ojos al mundo más allá de los prosaicos límites a los que la <br>mayoría está acostumbrada. En un esfuerzo por escapar de mi vida aventurera, más de una vez he intentado <br>formar una familia. Sin embargo, mis esfuerzos siempre han acabado en ruina, un precio que debo pagar por <br>los secretos que guardo. He perdido a seis amantes, todas asesinadas por enemigos y peligros que ingenuamente esperaba poder alejar de mi vida. Por eso me alisté voluntario en la Orden, hice un juramento para <br>eliminar la oscuridad de este mundo y busqué venganza por las vidas que me robaron.<br>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con <br>decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso <br>y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores <br>a los demás.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tTtwxG0vulYe2t7m","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Mi especialidad es la resolución de problemas y tengo talento <br>para analizar cualquier situación, lo que me permite encontrar <br>recursos y descubrir pistas. Gestionar el peligro requiere calma <br>y concentración, por lo que detesto actuar precipitadamente.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AWGAOp4Xnj0phGin","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>Utilizo estos conocimientos para descubrir verdades y desvelar <br>misterios. Odio los secretos, pero solo cuando no los conozco.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Lf0goSLVIuWIduYw","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con <br>decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso <br>y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores <br>a los demás.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2bGp7VfB9Fsj7koC","name":"Problem Solver","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Solucionador de problemas","description":"<p>si lo has visto una vez, <br>eres capaz de hacerlo tú mismo aún mejor. Puedes gastar 1 Soma <br>para replicar el efecto de un don de un Cazador o PNJ que hayas <br>visto durante el escenario. Los dones particulares pueden estar <br>fuera de los límites o solo producir una parte de su efecto, a discreción del Narrador. No puedes replicar más de un don a la vez. Una <br>vez por escena, puedes pedir al Narrador que te revele un don de <br>un PNJ que hayas tenido tiempo de estudiar.<br>Soy un hombre culto que ha estudiado las artes y las ciencias.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"If you’ve seen it once, you can do it yourself even better. You may spend 1 Soma to replicate the effect of a Gift from a Hunter or NPC you witnessed during the Scenario. Particular Gifts may still be off limits or only yield a part of their effect at the Storyteller’s discretion. You cannot replicate more than one Gift at a time. Once per Scene, you may ask the Storyteller to reveal to you a Gift of an NPC that you had time to study.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eURSbnxoP9vgXkJo","name":"The Key to Each Door","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"La llave para todas las puertas","description":"<p>una vez por escena, <br>puedes utilizar una de las llaves mágicas que tienes. Elige un efecto.<br>1. Abrir una puerta cerrada, sin importar cuántas cerraduras o defensas tenga.<br>2. Si un sujeto toca la llave, descubres la sensación más fuerte que <br>está experimentando.<br>3. Cerrar y bloquear una puerta para que ningún método convencional pueda abrirla.<br>4. Si pones una llave en la boca de un muerto, ves algunos de sus <br>recuerdos. El Narrador te los describirá, centrándose en tus áreas <br>de interés.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can use one of the magic keys you own. Choose an effect:\n1. Open a closed door, no matter how many locks or defenses it has.\n2. If a subject touches your key, discover the strongest feeling they are experiencing.\n3. Close and lock a door so that no conventional methods will be able to open it.\n4. If you put your key in the mouth of a dead person you will see some of their memories. The Storyteller will describe them to you, focusing on your areas of interest.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ER0lrlA7KIYDMrd0","name":"Dark Ego - The Unscrupulous Assassin","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro - El asesino sin escrúpulos","description":"<p>puedes parecer un <br>caballero civilizado, pero las apariencias engañan. Cuando sea necesario, no <br>dudarás en matar. Si eliminas a un PNJ infligiéndole la Herida final, también puedes eliminar inmediatamente a un segundo PNJ menor. Cuando te <br>defiendes con éxito de una acción violenta, puedes eliminar inmediatamente a un PNJ menor como respuesta. En cualquier caso, el objetivo debe estar <br>dentro del alcance de tu ira. Después de infligir 1 Herida a alguien, puedes <br>moverte libremente como acción adicional, lo que te permite alcanzar a <br>tu verdadero objetivo sin que nadie pueda impedírtelo.</p>","trigger":"revelar su lado oscuro hiriendo a alguien o actuando con agresividad a pesar de tu apariencia exterior tranquila y formal."}}}},"system":{"description":"You may appear as a civilized gentleman, but appearances can be deceiving. When necessary, you will not hesitate to kill. If you eliminate an NPC by inflicting a final Wound, you can also immediately eliminate a second Minor NPC. When you successfully defend yourself from a violent action, you can immediately eliminate a Minor NPC in response. Either way, the target must be within range of your wrath. After inflicting 1 Wound to someone, you can move freely as an additional action, allowing you to reach your true goal without anyone preventing you from doing so.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Reveal your dark side by injuring someone or acting aggressively despite your outwardly calm and staid appearance.","owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zXkd6txXbeLmRvya","name":"Nobleman’s clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ropas de noble","description":"<p>Ropas de noble</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Nobleman’s clothes","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LQSa5KAdEQreVzTA","name":"a long black cape","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una larga capa negra","description":"<p>Una larga capa negra</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a long black cape","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"f9v80xv1PzYLM1AJ","name":"a large bunch of keys","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un gran manojo de llaves","description":"<p>Un gran manojo de llaves</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a large bunch of keys","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nPFuylUnVoya1Gyg","name":"a fine dueling blade","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una fina espada de duelo","description":"<p>Una fina espada de duelo</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a fine dueling blade","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"djIibE9JfX7eRCUf","name":"snuff of excellent quality","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Rapé de excelente calidad","description":"<p>Rapé de excelente calidad</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"snuff of excellent quality","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eeQiiGwFSz2J0vTh","name":"a few doses of deadly Aqua Tofana","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Unas cuantas dosis de mortal agua tofana","description":"<p>Unas cuantas dosis de mortal agua tofana</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a few doses of deadly Aqua Tofana","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lQXQCLcc1FaRRtr8","name":"a large amount of coins and precious trinkets","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":7,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una gran cantidad de monedas y baratijas preciosas","description":"<p>Una gran cantidad de monedas y baratijas preciosas</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a large amount of coins and precious trinkets","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"e8sGxI3l3VLWjQ0K","name":"a heart-shaped locket hanging from a gold chain with the names of my lost loves engraved within","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment8.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"equipment","sequence":8,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un medallón en forma de corazón que cuelga de una cadena de oro, dentro del cual están grabados los nombres de mis amores perdidos.","description":"<p>Un medallón en forma de corazón que cuelga de una cadena de oro, dentro del cual están grabados los nombres de mis amores perdidos.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a heart-shaped locket hanging from a gold chain with the names of my lost loves engraved within","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","quantity":1,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment8.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"CgR6UL11zoAXqAeZ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28","owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-verdoux-bluebeard","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"28","contentKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Verdoux Barba Azul","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Verdoux Barba Azul","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>Soy un aristócrata francés, al que mi soberano llama para gestionar los asuntos más retorcidos y de peor reputación. He vivido una vida poco convencional, entre la realización de tareas imposibles y el mantenimiento <br>de secretos inconfesables, que me ha abierto los ojos al mundo más allá de los prosaicos límites a los que la <br>mayoría está acostumbrada. En un esfuerzo por escapar de mi vida aventurera, más de una vez he intentado <br>formar una familia. Sin embargo, mis esfuerzos siempre han acabado en ruina, un precio que debo pagar por <br>los secretos que guardo. He perdido a seis amantes, todas asesinadas por enemigos y peligros que ingenuamente esperaba poder alejar de mi vida. Por eso me alisté voluntario en la Orden, hice un juramento para <br>eliminar la oscuridad de este mundo y busqué venganza por las vidas que me robaron.<br>Bajo la fachada de un hombre respetable escondo a un hábil solucionador de problemas sin escrúpulos. Sé cómo matar y cómo actuar con <br>decisión. Todo el mundo ha hecho algo de lo que no se siente orgulloso <br>y no soporto ver a los hipócritas que fingen ser moralmente superiores <br>a los demás.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Verdoux Bluebeard","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1HWBZwitBJCoqXGF","name":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/yukie-onn-la-artista-viajera.webp","items":[{"_id":"BTLvdTBNqOxYt07B","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","description":"<p>S oy una artista viajera que ha conocido la fama y el honor en mi tierra natal, Japón. Sin embargo, ese prestigio no significó nada cuando encontré el amor verdadero con Akihiro, hijo de una poderosa familia noble. Cuando <br>le prohibieron verme, huimos juntos a la remota región de Ezo. Ni siquiera allí estuvimos fuera del alcance de la <br>familia de Akihiro y nos persiguieron hasta las altas montañas nevadas. Escapamos de todos los asesinos, pero <br>no pudimos burlar la tormenta de nieve que nos atrapó. Yo sobreviví, pero solo porque Akihiro sacrificó el calor de <br>su vida para salvar la mía. Pero el frío me ha cambiado. Se ha convertido en parte de mí y ahora lo único que puede <br>hacerme sentir calor es la sangre caliente de los demás. Tras vengarme de todos los que me arrebataron a Akihiro, <br>hui lejos, utilizando mi talento para el arte para obtener prestigio y la protección de ricos nobles occidentales. Ahora, <br>al servicio de la Orden, evito que otros sufran la injusticia que yo he padecido, castigando el egoísmo y la maldad.<br>Mi cuerpo es hielo puro y, por eso, puedo manipular el hielo a mi antojo. <br>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes <br>me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1EJlFTkhcY3fTnOs","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 1","description":"<p>Soy una artista muy hábil. La música, la danza y la pintura no <br>tienen misterios para mí. Mi encanto de otro mundo cautiva <br>a la gente corriente, llamando siempre la atención sobre mí.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"NKohhxMS5ipAyO2h","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Don 2","description":"<p>No puedo sentir dolor y mi frágil apariencia oculta sorprendentes aptitudes físicas. La sangre es lo único que puede proporcionarme calor y su aroma hace que me estremezca.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QT1PA6i9QJnFQ0C7","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","description":"<p>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes <br>me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"IY4fafMbJ2e0g50f","name":"Otherworldly Charm","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Encanto de otro mundo","description":"<p>cuando actúes o hagas alar -<br>de de tu talento, todas las miradas estarán puestas en ti. Obtienes <br>1 Éxito adicional por cada prueba de posición que realices para <br>atraer la atención o cautivar a alguien. Si obtienes un triunfo con <br>un incremento, puedes declarar que un sujeto que te ha visto se ha <br>enamorado de ti. El Narrador creará un objetivo específico para <br>ese sujeto que le hará buscar tu atención.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"When you perform or flaunt your talents, all eyes will be on you. Receive 1 Additional Success for each Position Check you make to attract attention or charm someone. If you get an Outcome with an Increment, you may declare that a subject who has seen you has fallen in love with you. The Storyteller will create a specific Agenda for them that leads them to seek your attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"bMqrs7jr59SODm4b","name":"Blood-Hot","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Sangre caliente","description":"<p>una vez por escena, puedes consumir <br>la sangre de una persona al infligirle una Herida no mortal. <br>Recuperas 1 Herida, 1 Soma y recibes alguna información sobre <br>tu víctima, como un recuerdo, una emoción o un deseo de su corazón. Cuando bebes sangre, tiras un dado: si sacas un 1, pierdes <br>el control y matas a la víctima absorbiendo su sangre, a menos que <br>alguien te lo impida.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can consume a person’s blood when inflicting 1 non-fatal Wound. You recover 1 Wound, 1 Soma and receive some information about your victim such as a memory, an emotion or their heart’s desire. When you drink blood roll a die: if you roll a 1, you lose control and you will kill your victim by draining their blood, unless someone stops you.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"6kZvNvxQCgZ7d4rM","name":"Dark Ego - Ice-Cold","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego oscuro – Fría como el hielo","description":"<p>tienes control sobre la temperatura de tu cuerpo y, en consecuencia, puedes congelar el entorno o los objetos que <br>se encuentren a tu alrededor. Cuando manipules hielo, elige un efecto creando <br>un descriptor que lo represente, como por ejemplo: Puerta congelada o Aura <br>de escarcha y gastar 1 Soma para manifestarlo durante toda la Escena. Como <br>efecto adicional, tu escarcha puede infligir 1 Herida a quienes interactúen con <br>ella o hacer que lo que congeles sea increíblemente frágil o increíblemente duro. <br>Quien explote los efectos de la escarcha a su favor obtiene 1 Éxito adicional para <br>su acción. Tu escarcha no tiene efecto directo sobre los seres vivos.</p>","trigger":"deshacerte de tu disfraz de artista sencillo y revelar tu verdadera \nforma, amargamente fría, o reaccionar con pasión cuando el miedo y la intimidación se utilicen por motivos egoístas."}}}},"system":{"description":"You have control over your body temperature and, consequently, you can freeze the environment or objects in your immediate vicinity. When you manipulate ice, choose an effect by creating a Descriptor that represents it such as: Frozen Door or Aura of Frost and spend 1 Soma to manifest it for the whole Scene. As an additional effect, your frost can inflict 1 Wound on those who interact with it or make what you freeze incredibly fragile or incredibly hard. Whoever exploits the effects of frost in their favor gains 1 Additional Success for their action. Your frost has no direct effect on living things.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Shed your disguise as a simple artist and reveal your true, bitterly cold form or react passionately when fear and intimidation are used for selfish reasons.","owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"omIn7Z4TVJWEndsk","name":"A travel kimono","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un kimono de viaje","description":"<p>Un kimono de viaje</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"A travel kimono","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"LBisyNxHNz1e0yf8","name":"a stage kimono and theatrical effects","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Kimono de escenario, maquillaje y efectos escénicos","description":"<p>Kimono de escenario, maquillaje y efectos escénicos</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a stage kimono and theatrical effects","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"PmIbH6GjJwM854p9","name":"a small ice sphere that never melts","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una pequeña esfera de hielo que nunca se derrite","description":"<p>Una pequeña esfera de hielo que nunca se derrite</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a small ice sphere that never melts","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"t3vrsciy2TH198Pv","name":"a butterfly-shaped hair clip (reminder of Akihiro)","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":4,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Una pinza para el pelo con forma de mariposa, recuerdo de mi amor perdido Akihiro","description":"<p>Una pinza para el pelo con forma de mariposa, recuerdo de mi amor perdido Akihiro</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a butterfly-shaped hair clip (reminder of Akihiro)","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ABe29oNv5j1e8FJH","name":"a finely crafted shamisen","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":5,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un shamisen finamente elaborado, un instrumento de cuerda tradicional","description":"<p>Un shamisen finamente elaborado, un instrumento de cuerda tradicional</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a finely crafted shamisen","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"VaVbjoXMDCavwWbo","name":"a pair of fine fans","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":6,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Varias dagas ocultas en el kimono","description":"<p>Varias dagas ocultas en el kimono</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"a pair of fine fans","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DozlNZJxl7TvpRPi","name":"several daggers hidden in the kimono","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"equipment","sequence":7,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Un par de abanicos de calidad.","description":"<p>Un par de abanicos de calidad.</p>"}}}},"system":{"description":"several daggers hidden in the kimono","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","quantity":1,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"DTrSj949Xt0rGwdJ","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book</strong></p><p>bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30","owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"source.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","pregenCollection":"Core Book","source":"bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"30","contentKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","system":{"details":{"concept":"Libro básico","origin":"Yukie Onn la Artista Viajera","role":"Cazador de la Orden","notes":"<p>S oy una artista viajera que ha conocido la fama y el honor en mi tierra natal, Japón. Sin embargo, ese prestigio no significó nada cuando encontré el amor verdadero con Akihiro, hijo de una poderosa familia noble. Cuando <br>le prohibieron verme, huimos juntos a la remota región de Ezo. Ni siquiera allí estuvimos fuera del alcance de la <br>familia de Akihiro y nos persiguieron hasta las altas montañas nevadas. Escapamos de todos los asesinos, pero <br>no pudimos burlar la tormenta de nieve que nos atrapó. Yo sobreviví, pero solo porque Akihiro sacrificó el calor de <br>su vida para salvar la mía. Pero el frío me ha cambiado. Se ha convertido en parte de mí y ahora lo único que puede <br>hacerme sentir calor es la sangre caliente de los demás. Tras vengarme de todos los que me arrebataron a Akihiro, <br>hui lejos, utilizando mi talento para el arte para obtener prestigio y la protección de ricos nobles occidentales. Ahora, <br>al servicio de la Orden, evito que otros sufran la injusticia que yo he padecido, castigando el egoísmo y la maldad.<br>Mi cuerpo es hielo puro y, por eso, puedo manipular el hielo a mi antojo. <br>Sin embargo, odio manifestar mi poder porque es peligroso para quienes <br>me rodean y, como artista, mi propósito es hacer sonreír a la gente.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6}}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book","origin":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qElrumnVfbpZH6oM","name":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/es-core/machiavelli-el-astuto-bischeri-el-malicioso.webp","items":[{"_id":"aGGXgbr4r7ocXiv4","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor principal","system":{"description":"Somos dos chicos que han sobrevivido y prosperado en las calles por medio del truco y el engaño. Desafortunadamente, cometimos un terrible error al elegir como objetivo a una anciana extraña: resultó ser una maldita bruja. Desde ese día, cada doce horas uno se vuelve zorro y el otro gato. Atados por este hechizo, encontramos un modo de ganar mucho dinero engañando a nobles estúpidos y mercaderes ricos. La Orden se ha fijado en nosotros y nos ha tomado bajo su ala, con la promesa de romper la maldición que nos aflige."}}}}},"system":{"description":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pshoDoCU0hwvbUA1","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Astuto","system":{"description":"Tengo un talento natural para decir mentiras, el cual la Orden usa para su beneficio. A pesar de mis orígenes, conozco mucho sobre muchas cosas porque mentir requiere planeación y preparación. Estoy tan acostumbrado a dar vueltas sin sentido que usualmente miento aun cuando no debería."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"4bx1MV4D1tjUluDx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Malicioso","system":{"description":"Una vida en el camino me enseñó a ser un ladrón talentoso, por lo que la Orden me usa para su trabajo sucio. Si puedo sacar ganancia de una situación, lo intentaré. \"Cada quien por su cuenta\" es mi dicho."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KCK7xOo63OhzOq3Z","name":"Descriptor 4","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor común","system":{"description":"No me detendré ante nada para obtener lo que quiero, y solo me toma unos segundos evaluar lo que está sucediendo y encontrar la forma adecuada para aprovecharme de ello. Detesto actuar solo porque no hay nadie a quien culpar."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"3ConSe0D2DgaQAHH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Descriptor de Ego Oscuro","system":{"description":"Nos guste o no, estamos atados por magia. Cada uno ve lo que el otro puede ver y, gracias a esto, podemos compartir pensamientos y trabajar juntos para engañar a otros. Quien está en forma animal detesta no poder comunicarse y a menudo molesta al otro sin rencores."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KADmiq2wuu9Cdr0z","name":"Believe in Miracles (Cunning)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Creer en milagros (Astuto)","system":{"description":"Una vez por escena, puedes decirles a todos algo que será aceptado sin preguntas hasta que la mentira sea descubierta. El engaño será obvio para tus víctimas al final de la escena o una vez expuesto. Recibes 1 Éxito adicional en cualquier tirada en la cual explotes la mentira que has creado."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can tell everyone something that will be accepted without question until the lie is uncovered. The deception becomes obvious at the end of the Scene or once exposed. Gain +1 Success on any Check where you exploit the lie.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pXvAH2XHNT6jsYEn","name":"Rogue (Sly)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ladrón (Malicioso)","system":{"description":"Siempre te aseguras de pasar desapercibido. Al fingir ser débil durante una escena, los PNJ te pasarán por alto como objetivo a menos que hayas actuado contra ellos previamente. Gastando 1 Soma, puedes huir de una escena o de una situación donde haya multitud. Nadie será capaz de detenerte."}}}}},"system":{"description":"By pretending to be weak during a Scene, NPCs will overlook you unless you acted against them. By spending 1 Soma, you can flee any Scene involving a crowd.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JTMldAqO31DdaXn7","name":"Partner in Crime (Common)","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Socio del crimen (común)","system":{"description":"Una vez por escena, si uno de tus aliados actúa con tu apoyo, recibe 1 Éxito adicional a sus tiradas. Además, una vez por escena, si uno de tus aliados logra un resultado con un Incremento después de haber completado su acción, puedes tomar una acción adicional inmediatamente."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, when an ally acts with your support, they receive +1 Additional Success. Additionally, if an ally achieves an Outcome with an Increment, you may immediately take an extra action.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hdn18U2N1IPIptNH","name":"Dark Ego - The Fox and the Cat","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Ego Oscuro - El Zorro y el Gato","system":{"description":"La maldición que te une te convierte en un equipo perfecto. En la noche como Astuto o durante el día como Malicioso, eres humano y haces pleno uso del apoyo de tu socio en su forma animal. Tu socio puede actuar individualmente para completar una tarea que le des. Comparten las mismas Heridas y el mismo Soma. Quien esté en forma humana puede gastar 1 Soma para usar el Don de su cómplice. Una vez por escena, si tu socio está ahí para ayudarte, recibes 2 Éxitos adicionales a tu tirada de Posición.","trigger":"Haz un truco o engaña a alguien tomando ventaja del apoyo de tu leal socio del crimen."}}}}},"system":{"description":"You and your partner share Soma and Wounds. The human form can spend 1 Soma to use the Gift of the animal form. Once per Scene, if your partner helps you, you gain +2 Additional Successes on a Position Check.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Trick or deceive someone, taking advantage of your partner's support.","owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ypAzQzRrCsqHF5Io","name":"Night (Cunning): Comfortable and light clothes, hidden small knives, counterfeit cards and stamps, fake coins and jewelry","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"equipment","sequence":1,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Equipo de Astuto","system":{"description":"Ropas ligeras y cómodas; un set de pequeños cuchillos escondidos por doquier; cartas, estampas y otros objetos falsos; algunas monedas y joyas falsas; un volumen de la Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana, que siempre revela lo que necesito saber."}}}}},"system":{"description":"Night (Cunning): Comfortable and light clothes, hidden small knives, counterfeit cards and stamps, fake coins and jewelry","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"415H5xYcYMCGJCxx","name":"a volume of the Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana Encyclopedia. Day (Sly): Worn-out clothes, sharp long knife","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"equipment","sequence":2,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Equipo de Malicioso","system":{"description":"Ropas desgastadas y maltrechas; una daga larga y afilada; un viejo palo para fingir estar ciego; una vieja bolsa con un agujero; un saco lleno de chatarra recolectada mientras robo."}}}}},"system":{"description":"a volume of the Biblioteca Universale Sacro-Profana Encyclopedia. Day (Sly): Worn-out clothes, sharp long knife","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wTzsw35p5XOr8yam","name":"old stick to pretend to be blind, torn purse with a hole, sack full of stolen junk","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"equipment","sequence":3,"translations":{"es":{"name":"Nota de cambio","system":{"description":"Durante la noche usa el Descriptor, Don y equipo de Astuto, mientras Malicioso será un gato. Durante el día usa el Descriptor, Don y equipo de Malicioso, mientras Astuto será un zorro."}}}}},"system":{"description":"old stick to pretend to be blind, torn purse with a hole, sack full of stolen junk","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","quantity":1,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"JW02B5MZvlxEeiHP","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Core Book: Fox and Cat</strong></p><p>bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.</p><p>Use Cunning's side at night and Sly's side during the day, following the source sheet. Spanish local sheet archived at systems/broken-tales/assets/source-pdfs/machiavelli-el-zorro-astuto-y-bischeri-el-gato-malicioso.pdf.</p>","notes":"bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2","owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"source.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"core-book-fox-and-cat-cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","pregenCollection":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","source":"bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf","pages":"2","contentKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","language":"en","avatarLanguage":"es","translations":{"es":{"name":"Machiavelli el Zorro Astuto y Bischeri el Gato Malicioso","system":{"details":{"notes":"Somos dos chicos que han sobrevivido y prosperado en las calles por medio del truco y el engaño. Desafortunadamente, cometimos un terrible error al elegir como objetivo a una anciana extraña: resultó ser una maldita bruja. Desde ese día, cada doce horas uno se vuelve zorro y el otro gato. Atados por este hechizo, encontramos un modo de ganar mucho dinero engañando a nobles estúpidos y mercaderes ricos. La Orden se ha fijado en nosotros y nos ha tomado bajo su ala, con la promesa de romper la maldición que nos aflige."}}}}}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","origin":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
